  <head>
    <title>设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）第四章  中国古代建筑史</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <outline text="设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第四章     中国古代建筑史" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E7%AB%A0%20%20%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%B2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国建筑是世界上传统延续最长的建筑体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E5%BB%B6%E7%BB%AD%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="这一方面是因为中国的封建社会时期特别长，社会变化缓慢；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E7%BC%93%E6%85%A2%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另一方面是中国的地理环境比较封闭，周边有大海、高山、沙漠的阻隔，在交通不便的古代，很少受到很大的外来影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%81%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%98%BB%E9%9A%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%8D%E4%BE%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%91%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E6%9D%A5%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="更因为中国的文化一般高于相邻国家或民族的文化，即使某些外来因素传入中国，也会很自然地融入，而成为中国自己的东西。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9B%B4%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%8E%E7%9B%B8%E9%82%BB%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%96%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%E6%9F%90%E4%BA%9B%E5%A4%96%E6%9D%A5%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%88%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%9E%8D%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国建筑自其萌芽，直到今世，一脉相承，可以说是具有很大的稳定性，与历史上西欧建筑的剧烈变化大不相同。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%87%AA%E5%85%B6%E8%90%8C%E8%8A%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%8A%E4%B8%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%84%89%E7%9B%B8%E6%89%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A5%BF%E6%AC%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%89%A7%E7%83%88%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国古代建筑是中国传统文化的重要组成部分，与中医、国画、民乐等相似，有中国自己特有的传统，是延续数千年的独特体系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%BB%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%BB%E3%80%81%E6%B0%91%E4%B9%90%E7%AD%89%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%B6%E7%BB%AD%E6%95%B0%E5%8D%83%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="从都城的规划建设，到建筑的设计施工，乃至于装修装饰，都有自己的理论与方法，在世界上独树一帜，有着很卓越的成就。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%83%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%8E%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E7%8B%AC%E6%A0%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%9C%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%80%E5%BE%88%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="它不仅是珍贵的历史文化遗产，认真加以研究总结，还可以为当今的建设提供可贵的借鉴。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E6%98%AF%E7%8F%8D%E8%B4%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A4%E7%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%AF%E8%B4%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%80%9F%E9%89%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第一节     中国古代建筑的发展历程" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="一、原始社会时期（约距今9000~4000年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E7%BA%A6%E8%B7%9D%E4%BB%8A9000~4000%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在新石器时代的后期，人类从栖息手巢与穴，进步到有意识地建造房屋，出现了干阑式与木骨泥墙的房屋。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9F%B3%E5%99%A8%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E4%BB%8E%E6%A0%96%E6%81%AF%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A2%E4%B8%8E%E7%A9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%B9%B2%E9%98%91%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%A8%E9%AA%A8%E6%B3%A5%E5%A2%99%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="干阑的实例如浙江余姚河姆渡村发现的建筑遗址，距今约六七千年，已有椎卯技术。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B2%E9%98%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E4%BD%99%E5%A7%9A%E6%B2%B3%E5%A7%86%E6%B8%A1%E6%9D%91%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%9D%E4%BB%8A%E7%BA%A6%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%83%E5%8D%83%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E6%A4%8E%E5%8D%AF%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="木骨泥墙房屋实例以西安半坡村和陕西临潼姜寨最具代表性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%A8%E9%AA%A8%E6%B3%A5%E5%A2%99%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E4%BB%A5%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%8A%E5%9D%A1%E6%9D%91%E5%92%8C%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%B4%E6%BD%BC%E5%A7%9C%E5%AF%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%85%B7%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="姜寨有五座“大房子”共同面向一个广场，每座“大房子”周围环绕着若干或圆或方的小房子，其布局反映了母系氏族社会聚落的特色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A7%9C%E5%AF%A8%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%94%E5%BA%A7%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%E2%80%9D%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E5%BA%A7%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%E2%80%9D%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E7%9D%80%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E6%88%96%E5%9C%86%E6%88%96%E6%96%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E6%AF%8D%E7%B3%BB%E6%B0%8F%E6%97%8F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%81%9A%E8%90%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="二者属于仰韶文化时期的居住遗址，其中的“大房子”是仰韶文化时期母系氏族社会议事的地方。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E8%80%85%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%B0%E9%9F%B6%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%B0%E9%9F%B6%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E6%AF%8D%E7%B3%BB%E6%B0%8F%E6%97%8F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE%E4%BA%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="龙山文化时期的居住遗址以西安客省庄的一座吕字形平面的房屋为例，房屋面积比仰韶时期的变小，室内有供存贮的窖穴，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%BE%99%E5%B1%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%AE%A2%E7%9C%81%E5%BA%84%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%90%95%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%AF%94%E4%BB%B0%E9%9F%B6%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%AD%98%E8%B4%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AA%96%E7%A9%B4%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="表现了父系氏族社会私有财产的出现，建筑技术的进步是地面上铺有“白灰面”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E7%88%B6%E7%B3%BB%E6%B0%8F%E6%97%8F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E8%B4%A2%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8A%E9%93%BA%E6%9C%89%E2%80%9C%E7%99%BD%E7%81%B0%E9%9D%A2%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="近年在浙江余杭区的瑶山与汇观山发现有祭坛，为土筑的，呈长方形。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%A8%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E4%BD%99%E6%9D%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%91%B6%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%8E%E6%B1%87%E8%A7%82%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E7%A5%AD%E5%9D%9B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%9F%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%88%E9%95%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在内蒙古大青山和辽宁喀左县东山嘴发现用石块堆成的方形和圆形的祭坛；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%85%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E5%92%8C%E8%BE%BD%E5%AE%81%E5%96%80%E5%B7%A6%E5%8E%BF%E4%B8%9C%E5%B1%B1%E5%98%B4%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%94%A8%E7%9F%B3%E5%9D%97%E5%A0%86%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%86%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%AD%E5%9D%9B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在辽宁建平县发现了一处内中有女神像的中国最古老的神庙遗址。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%BE%BD%E5%AE%81%E5%BB%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%8E%BF%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E5%86%85%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%83%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%80%E5%8F%A4%E8%80%81%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%9E%E5%BA%99%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="这些考古发现，使人们对于中国原始社会的建筑水平，有了进一步的了解。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="二、奴隶社会时期（公元前21世纪~前476年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D21%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA~%E5%89%8D476%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此阶段包括夏、商、西周、春秋时期。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%8F%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E3%80%81%E8%A5%BF%E5%91%A8%E3%80%81%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）夏（约公元前2070~前1600年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%8F%EF%BC%88%E7%BA%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D2070~%E5%89%8D1600%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="夏代的城市遗址在河南王城岗、山西夏县及河南淮阳平粮台有所发现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E5%9C%A8%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B2%97%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%8F%E5%8E%BF%E5%8F%8A%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E6%B7%AE%E9%98%B3%E5%B9%B3%E7%B2%AE%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="有人认为河南偃师市二里头遗址是夏代都城之一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%81%83%E5%B8%88%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%8C%E9%87%8C%E5%A4%B4%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%8F%E4%BB%A3%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="已发现宫殿遗址两处，其中一号宫殿最大，是我国迄今发现的规模较大的廊院式建筑，二号宫殿是一更为完整的廊院式建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%8A%E9%99%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%B7%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%8A%E9%99%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）商（公元前1600~前1046年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%95%86%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D1600~%E5%89%8D1046%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="商代是我国奴隶社会大发展的时期，青铜工艺已达到纯熟程度，已有甲骨文等文字记述的历史。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%BB%A3%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%92%E9%93%9C%E5%B7%A5%E8%89%BA%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%BA%AF%E7%86%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E7%94%B2%E9%AA%A8%E6%96%87%E7%AD%89%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="建筑技术明显提高。著名遗址有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①郑州商城，可能是商王仲丁时的傲都。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E9%83%91%E5%B7%9E%E5%95%86%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%95%86%E7%8E%8B%E4%BB%B2%E4%B8%81%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%82%B2%E9%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②黄陂盘龙城商城遗址，夯土台基上平行排列三座殿堂，可能是商代某一诸侯国的宫殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E9%BB%84%E9%99%82%E7%9B%98%E9%BE%99%E5%9F%8E%E5%95%86%E5%9F%8E%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%AF%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E6%AE%BF%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%95%86%E4%BB%A3%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%80%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③河南偃师市尸乡沟早商城址。已发掘出两座庭院式建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%81%83%E5%B8%88%E5%B8%82%E5%B0%B8%E4%B9%A1%E6%B2%9F%E6%97%A9%E5%95%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%9D%80%E3%80%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%A4%E5%BA%A7%E5%BA%AD%E9%99%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④殷墟，是商代晚期的都城遗址，位于河南安阳小屯村。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E6%AE%B7%E5%A2%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%95%86%E4%BB%A3%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%B1%AF%E6%9D%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国考古界多年来对殷墟做过细致的考古发掘工作，对于它的宫殿、墓葬等已有较清楚的认识。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%E5%AF%B9%E6%AE%B7%E5%A2%9F%E5%81%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%86%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%A2%93%E8%91%AC%E7%AD%89%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E8%BE%83%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它的建筑建于长方形土台上，长面朝前，有纵有横，说明布局已具庭院的雏形。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%8E%E9%95%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%95%BF%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%9D%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%BA%B5%E6%9C%89%E6%A8%AA%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%B7%E5%BA%AD%E9%99%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%8F%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它的墓葬为土扩木梓墓，深达十几米，四出羡道，有很多殉葬的人与物。安阳殷墟已列入世界文化遗产名录。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%93%E8%91%AC%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%9F%E6%89%A9%E6%9C%A8%E6%A2%93%E5%A2%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%B7%B1%E8%BE%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%87%A0%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%9B%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%A1%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E6%AE%89%E8%91%AC%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E3%80%82%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B3%E6%AE%B7%E5%A2%9F%E5%B7%B2%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%90%8D%E5%BD%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）西周（公元前1046~前771年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E8%A5%BF%E5%91%A8%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D1046~%E5%89%8D771%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="西周时在奴隶主内部已有按宗法分封的制度，规定了严格的等级。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E5%91%A8%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6%E4%B8%BB%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E6%8C%89%E5%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%88%86%E5%B0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%A5%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="表现在城市的规模上就是诸侯的城按公、侯、伯、子、男的等级，分别不准超过王城的1/3、1/5、1/9。否则即是“越”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E6%8C%89%E5%85%AC%E3%80%81%E4%BE%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BC%AF%E3%80%81%E5%AD%90%E3%80%81%E7%94%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%841/3%E3%80%811/5%E3%80%811/9%E3%80%82%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E5%8D%B3%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E8%B6%8A%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="西周最具代表性的建筑遗址是陕西岐山凤维村的“中国第一四合院”，是一处二进院的宗庙建筑。另外在湖北斯春出土了一处建筑遗址，为干阑式建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%85%B7%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E6%98%AF%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E5%B2%90%E5%B1%B1%E5%87%A4%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%91%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%88%E9%99%A2%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%97%E5%BA%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%A8%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E6%96%AF%E6%98%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%B9%B2%E9%98%91%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="西周在建筑上突出的成就是瓦的发明，使建筑脱离了“茅茨土阶”的简陋状态。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E5%91%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8A%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%93%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E8%8C%85%E8%8C%A8%E5%9C%9F%E9%98%B6%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E9%99%8B%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）春秋（公元前770~前476年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D770~%E5%89%8D476%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="春秋时期宫殿建筑的特色是“高台榭、美宫室”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%B0%E6%A6%AD%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%AB%E5%AE%A4%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="这一方面是高台建筑有利于防刺客、防洪水、可供帝王享受登临之乐；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%B2%E5%88%BA%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E4%BE%9B%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E7%99%BB%E4%B8%B4%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%90%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="另一方面也是由于建筑技术的原因，当时要修建高大的建筑，要依傍土台才能建造成功。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E5%82%8D%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="近年对秦国都城雍城的考古工作中出土了36cm×14cm×6cm的青灰色砖和质地坚硬有花纹的空心砖，说明我国早在春秋时期已开始了用砖的历史。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%A6%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E9%9B%8D%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E4%BA%8636cm%C3%9714cm%C3%976cm%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E7%A0%96%E5%92%8C%E8%B4%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%9A%E7%A1%AC%E6%9C%89%E8%8A%B1%E7%BA%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E5%BF%83%E7%A0%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%A9%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E5%B7%B2%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%86%E7%94%A8%E7%A0%96%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此时期杰出的工匠为公输般——鲁班（姓公输，名般，鲁国人，因古时“般”与“班”通用，故又常被后人称为鲁班），被后世奉为多种行业工匠的祖师爷。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E6%9D%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%AC%E8%BE%93%E8%88%AC%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%B2%81%E7%8F%AD%EF%BC%88%E5%A7%93%E5%85%AC%E8%BE%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8D%E8%88%AC%EF%BC%8C%E9%B2%81%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%A4%E6%97%B6%E2%80%9C%E8%88%AC%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%8E%E2%80%9C%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%8F%88%E5%B8%B8%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E9%B2%81%E7%8F%AD%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%96%E5%A5%89%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E7%88%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="三、封建社会初期（公元前475~公元581年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D475~%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83581%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此阶段包括：战国、秦、汉、三国、两晋、南北朝。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%81%E7%A7%A6%E3%80%81%E6%B1%89%E3%80%81%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%81%E4%B8%A4%E6%99%8B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）战国（公元前475~前221年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D475~%E5%89%8D221%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="战国时战乱频仍，“筑城以卫君，造郭以守民”，此前对诸侯国城址大小的限制已失去控制。城市规模扩大是这一时期的特点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%88%98%E4%B9%B1%E9%A2%91%E4%BB%8D%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%AD%91%E5%9F%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%AB%E5%90%9B%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E9%83%AD%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%88%E6%B0%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%AF%B9%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%9D%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%B7%B2%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="战国七雄各国的都城都很大，以齐国的临淄为例：大城南北长5km、东西宽约4km，城内居民达7万户，街道上车毂相碰，人肩相摩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%83%E9%9B%84%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E9%83%BD%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%BD%90%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%B4%E6%B7%84%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E9%95%BF5km%E3%80%81%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%BD%E7%BA%A64km%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%BE%BE7%E4%B8%87%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8A%E8%BD%A6%E6%AF%82%E7%9B%B8%E7%A2%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%82%A9%E7%9B%B8%E6%91%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="大城西南角有小城，推测是齐国宫殿所在地，其中有高达16m的夯土台。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E8%A7%92%E6%9C%89%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%8B%E6%98%AF%E9%BD%90%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E8%BE%BE16m%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%AF%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在陕西咸阳市东郊发掘的秦咸阳一号宫殿是一座以夯土台为核心，周围用空间较小的木构架建筑环绕的台榭式建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E5%92%B8%E9%98%B3%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%9C%E9%83%8A%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%A6%E5%92%B8%E9%98%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AF%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%B0%E6%A6%AD%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="该建筑具有采暖、排水、冷藏、洗浴等设施，显示了战国时期高级建筑已达到的水平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%86%B7%E8%97%8F%E3%80%81%E6%B4%97%E6%B5%B4%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="当时的木工技术，从近年河南、湖南等地出土的战国墓的棺梓上，可看到已有形式多样的榫卯，说明木工已达到很高的水平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E3%80%81%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E5%A2%93%E7%9A%84%E6%A3%BA%E6%A2%93%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%AB%E5%8D%AF%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%B7%B2%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%BE%88%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="在河北平山县的战国中山王馨的墓中出土了一块铜板错银的“兆域图”，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%B1%E5%8E%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E7%8E%8B%E9%A6%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%9D%97%E9%93%9C%E6%9D%BF%E9%94%99%E9%93%B6%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%85%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="该图大体上是按一定比例制作的，有名称、尺寸、地形位置的说明，并有国王诏令。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E5%9B%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%8B%E8%AF%8F%E4%BB%A4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此图被誉为中国现在已知的最早的建筑总平面图。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%89%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）秦（公元前221~前206年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E7%A7%A6%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D221~%E5%89%8D206%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="秦始皇灭六国，统一天下。他每灭一国，就在咸阳北坂上仿建那一国的宫室，这在建筑技术、建筑风格上起到了交流融会作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87%E7%81%AD%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%82%E4%BB%96%E6%AF%8F%E7%81%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%A8%E5%92%B8%E9%98%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%9D%82%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%BF%E5%BB%BA%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8A%E8%B5%B7%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E8%9E%8D%E4%BC%9A%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="秦代的都城与宫殿均不遵周礼，而是在跨渭水南北广阔地区，弥山跨谷地修建。脍炙人口的阿房宫是秦始皇拟建的朝宫的前殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%A6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%B5%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E8%B7%A8%E6%B8%AD%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E5%B9%BF%E9%98%94%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%A5%E5%B1%B1%E8%B7%A8%E8%B0%B7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%E8%84%8D%E7%82%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%98%BF%E6%88%BF%E5%AE%AB%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87%E6%8B%9F%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9D%E5%AE%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="《史记》记载：“先作前殿阿房，东西五百步，南北五十丈，上可以坐万人，下可以建五丈旗。周驰为阁道，自殿下直抵南山。表南山之巅以为阙。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%B2%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%85%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%89%8D%E6%AE%BF%E9%98%BF%E6%88%BF%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E7%99%BE%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9D%90%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%88%E6%97%97%E3%80%82%E5%91%A8%E9%A9%B0%E4%B8%BA%E9%98%81%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BF%E4%B8%8B%E7%9B%B4%E6%8A%B5%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%82%E8%A1%A8%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1%E4%B9%8B%E5%B7%85%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E9%98%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="络为复道，自阿房渡渭、属之咸阳……”把数千米以外的天然地形，组织到建筑空间中来。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%8D%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E9%98%BF%E6%88%BF%E6%B8%A1%E6%B8%AD%E3%80%81%E5%B1%9E%E4%B9%8B%E5%92%B8%E9%98%B3%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%E6%8A%8A%E6%95%B0%E5%8D%83%E7%B1%B3%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%88%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这种超尺度的构图手法，气魄之大，正是秦这个伟大帝国气势的反映。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E8%B6%85%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%B0%94%E9%AD%84%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A3%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%A6%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BC%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%94%E5%8A%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="秦始皇的陵墓一—骊山陵，尚未进行考古发掘，陵体遗存边长350余米，残高仍在43m以上。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87%E7%9A%84%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E9%AA%8A%E5%B1%B1%E9%99%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%B5%E4%BD%93%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E8%BE%B9%E9%95%BF350%E4%BD%99%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E9%AB%98%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A843m%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="附近农民耕地时，常有一些建筑构件出土，近年在墓东侧发掘出的“兵马俑”，轰动世界，“秦俑学”已成为一种专门学科。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%80%95%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%A8%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%9C%E4%BE%A7%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%85%B5%E9%A9%AC%E4%BF%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BD%B0%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%A7%A6%E4%BF%91%E5%AD%A6%E2%80%9D%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="史书中说墓中具有天文地理、宫观百官、奇珍异宝，当非臆测。修驰道、筑长城、也是秦代的重要建设。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%B4%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E5%AE%AB%E8%A7%82%E7%99%BE%E5%AE%98%E3%80%81%E5%A5%87%E7%8F%8D%E5%BC%82%E5%AE%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E9%9D%9E%E8%87%86%E6%B5%8B%E3%80%82%E4%BF%AE%E9%A9%B0%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E7%AD%91%E9%95%BF%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%A6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）汉（公元前206~公元220年，包括王莽新朝）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E6%B1%89%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D206~%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83220%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%8E%8B%E8%8E%BD%E6%96%B0%E6%9C%9D%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="西汉在渭水南岸建长安城，其中包括了秦代未毁的部分宫殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%B1%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AD%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%97%E5%B2%B8%E5%BB%BA%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BA%86%E7%A7%A6%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%AA%E6%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="又受地形限制，城市的外轮廓曲折，附会为北像北斗、南像南斗，俗称“斗城”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E8%BD%AE%E5%BB%93%E6%9B%B2%E6%8A%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%84%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E5%8C%97%E5%83%8F%E5%8C%97%E6%96%97%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E5%83%8F%E5%8D%97%E6%96%97%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E6%96%97%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城内布局全未按礼制对都城的规定，宫殿与民居杂处。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%AA%E6%8C%89%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%AF%B9%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E6%9D%82%E5%A4%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="全城面积36km2，有城门12座，城内有五座宫城、八街九陌、168闯里。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF36km2%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%8E%E9%97%A812%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%94%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E5%85%AB%E8%A1%97%E4%B9%9D%E9%99%8C%E3%80%81168%E9%97%AF%E9%87%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在汉长安南郊出土了11座“礼制建筑”，应为王莽九庙遗址。其中一座周边有圈水的建筑，仍属有土台核心的木构建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B1%89%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%97%E9%83%8A%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E4%BA%8611%E5%BA%A7%E2%80%9C%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA%E7%8E%8B%E8%8E%BD%E4%B9%9D%E5%BA%99%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%88%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8D%E5%B1%9E%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%B0%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="汉代的陵墓仍属土扩木梓墓，用“黄肠题凑”。陵侧建陵邑，迁各地豪富及外戚等来居住。名为替先帝守陵，实为强干弱枝，便于控制管理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E4%BB%8D%E5%B1%9E%E5%9C%9F%E6%89%A9%E6%9C%A8%E6%A2%93%E5%A2%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E9%BB%84%E8%82%A0%E9%A2%98%E5%87%91%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%E9%99%B5%E4%BE%A7%E5%BB%BA%E9%99%B5%E9%82%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%81%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E8%B1%AA%E5%AF%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%96%E6%88%9A%E7%AD%89%E6%9D%A5%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E3%80%82%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%BA%E6%9B%BF%E5%85%88%E5%B8%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%99%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%BA%E5%B9%B2%E5%BC%B1%E6%9E%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="汉代陵邑共有七座，其中以长陵、安陵、阳陵、茂陵、平陵最著名，称“五陵”，后来诗文中常以五陵喻为一种豪门聚居之地，内中子弟称五陵少年”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%B5%E9%82%91%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%83%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%A5%E9%95%BF%E9%99%B5%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E9%99%B5%E3%80%81%E9%98%B3%E9%99%B5%E3%80%81%E8%8C%82%E9%99%B5%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E9%99%B5%E6%9C%80%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%94%E9%99%B5%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E8%AF%97%E6%96%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%94%E9%99%B5%E5%96%BB%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E8%B1%AA%E9%97%A8%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%9F%E7%A7%B0%E4%BA%94%E9%99%B5%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="东汉于公元25年定都洛阳。都城内有东西二宫两宫之间以阁道相通。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%8325%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%9A%E9%83%BD%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E3%80%82%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%AB%E4%B8%A4%E5%AE%AB%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%81%E9%81%93%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="文献上记载东汉的宫室中有椒房、温室殿、冰室等防寒祛暑的房屋，说明建筑的进步，已然注意到居住条件的改善。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E4%B8%8A%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E5%AE%A4%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E6%A4%92%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E6%B8%A9%E5%AE%A4%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E9%98%B2%E5%AF%92%E7%A5%9B%E6%9A%91%E7%9A%84%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E7%84%B6%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%88%B0%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="汉代遗存至今的地面以上建筑有墓前的石阙、墓表、石享堂、石象生，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%89%E5%A2%93%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E9%98%99%E3%80%81%E5%A2%93%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E4%BA%AB%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E8%B1%A1%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如：四川雅安高颐墓阙、北京西郊东汉幽州书佐秦君墓表、山东肥城孝堂山郭巨墓石享堂等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E9%9B%85%E5%AE%89%E9%AB%98%E9%A2%90%E5%A2%93%E9%98%99%E3%80%81%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%8A%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89%E5%B9%BD%E5%B7%9E%E4%B9%A6%E4%BD%90%E7%A7%A6%E5%90%9B%E5%A2%93%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E8%82%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%AD%9D%E5%A0%82%E5%B1%B1%E9%83%AD%E5%B7%A8%E5%A2%93%E7%9F%B3%E4%BA%AB%E5%A0%82%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另外就是崖墓、砖石墓等中的明器、画像砖、画像石、壁画等间接的建筑形象资料。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B4%96%E5%A2%93%E3%80%81%E7%A0%96%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%93%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E5%99%A8%E3%80%81%E7%94%BB%E5%83%8F%E7%A0%96%E3%80%81%E7%94%BB%E5%83%8F%E7%9F%B3%E3%80%81%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E7%AD%89%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="石墓中的石制仿木构件，显示了一些汉代建筑信息，但因石与木性质的不同，形象表现受局限，只能供参考。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9F%B3%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%BF%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%9B%A0%E7%9F%B3%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%8F%97%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）三国（公元220~265年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83220~265%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此时期是东汉末魏、蜀、吴三国鼎立的战乱年代。位于河北临漳县的邺城，原是齐柜公所置的城，后属晋。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89%E6%9C%AB%E9%AD%8F%E3%80%81%E8%9C%80%E3%80%81%E5%90%B4%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E9%BC%8E%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E4%B9%B1%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%82%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%B4%E6%BC%B3%E5%8E%BF%E7%9A%84%E9%82%BA%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%BD%90%E6%9F%9C%E5%85%AC%E6%89%80%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E5%B1%9E%E6%99%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="三国时曹操以此为南征北战的大本营，城市的建设具有新的格局，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%9B%B9%E6%93%8D%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%97%E5%BE%81%E5%8C%97%E6%88%98%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%AC%E8%90%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="文献上对此城记述颇多，城的面积为6.5km2，有中轴线，有明确的分区，是中国第一座轮廓方正的都城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E4%B8%8A%E5%AF%B9%E6%AD%A4%E5%9F%8E%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E9%A2%87%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%BA6.5km2%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%BD%AE%E5%BB%93%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此城早已毁于兵羹，再加上漳河屡次泛滥，地上遗存已很少，有人认为它是隋唐长安城的蓝本。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%9F%8E%E6%97%A9%E5%B7%B2%E6%AF%81%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%B5%E7%BE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B3%E6%B2%B3%E5%B1%A1%E6%AC%A1%E6%B3%9B%E6%BB%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8A%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E5%B7%B2%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%83%E6%98%AF%E9%9A%8B%E5%94%90%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%93%9D%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）两晋、南北朝（公元265~581年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%A4%E6%99%8B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83265~581%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="此阶段包括：西晋" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%A5%BF%E6%99%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="十六国、北魏" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%81%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="东魏一北齐" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E9%AD%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%8C%97%E9%BD%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="西魏一北周" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E9%AD%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%8C%97%E5%91%A8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="东晋、宋、齐、梁、陈" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E6%99%8B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%81%E9%BD%90%E3%80%81%E6%A2%81%E3%80%81%E9%99%88%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="佛寺、佛塔及石窟寺的出现，是本时期建筑最大的成就。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BD%9B%E5%A1%94%E5%8F%8A%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="佛教虽然于西汉末年已传入中国，但未兴盛。直到此时，由于战乱，百姓不堪其苦，寄希望于来世；帝王崇佛，大力提倡佛教，佛教才得以大兴。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E8%99%BD%E7%84%B6%E4%BA%8E%E8%A5%BF%E6%B1%89%E6%9C%AB%E5%B9%B4%E5%B7%B2%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%9C%AA%E5%85%B4%E7%9B%9B%E3%80%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%98%E4%B9%B1%EF%BC%8C%E7%99%BE%E5%A7%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%A0%AA%E5%85%B6%E8%8B%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%84%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BA%8E%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%96%EF%BC%9B%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E5%B4%87%E4%BD%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%9B%E6%8F%90%E5%80%A1%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E6%89%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="文献记载：南朝佛寺有500余所，北朝仅洛阳一地，就有佛寺1367所。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%9D%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E6%9C%89500%E4%BD%99%E6%89%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%85%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA1367%E6%89%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="公元516年，北魏胡灵太后在洛阳建的永宁寺塔，是一座方形平面的9层木塔，高达40余丈，《洛阳伽蓝记》对其描述甚详。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83516%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E8%83%A1%E7%81%B5%E5%A4%AA%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B8%E5%AE%81%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%849%E5%B1%82%E6%9C%A8%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%98%E8%BE%BE40%E4%BD%99%E4%B8%88%EF%BC%8C%E3%80%8A%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E4%BC%BD%E8%93%9D%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%E7%94%9A%E8%AF%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="现存的河南登封嵩山嵩岳寺塔，建于北魏正光四年（公元523年），是一座15层的密檐式塔，是我国地面之上真正的建筑遗存中最早的一座。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%81%E5%B5%A9%E5%B1%B1%E5%B5%A9%E5%B2%B3%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E6%AD%A3%E5%85%89%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83523%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A715%E5%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E6%AA%90%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="石窟寺自印度传入，与中国开凿崖墓技术结合，很快地得到推广。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BC%80%E5%87%BF%E5%B4%96%E5%A2%93%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E5%9C%B0%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="敦煌莫高窟、大同云冈石窟、洛阳龙门石窟是最著名的三处。石窟中有许多反映当时建筑形象的雕刻，如塔、殿宇的屋顶、斗棋、柱等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%95%A6%E7%85%8C%E8%8E%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%AA%9F%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%86%88%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E3%80%81%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E9%BE%99%E9%97%A8%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%84%E3%80%82%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%95%E5%88%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E6%AE%BF%E5%AE%87%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E3%80%81%E6%9F%B1%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="在河北定兴有一座北齐的义慈惠石柱、柱顶上有一座小殿，有梭柱、平直檐口、屋面瓦脊等建筑细部的形象，是研究北朝建筑的重要资料。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%8C%97%E9%BD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%89%E6%85%88%E6%83%A0%E7%9F%B3%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%81%E6%9F%B1%E9%A1%B6%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%B0%8F%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%A2%AD%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B4%E6%AA%90%E5%8F%A3%E3%80%81%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%93%A6%E8%84%8A%E7%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%86%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="南朝仅存有陵墓，以地面上的石刻墓表及石象生、辟邪较为出色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%85%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%89%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%BB%E5%A2%93%E8%A1%A8%E5%8F%8A%E7%9F%B3%E8%B1%A1%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E8%BE%9F%E9%82%AA%E8%BE%83%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="综观此阶段历时900余年，以汉代为高潮。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BC%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8E%86%E6%97%B6900%E4%BD%99%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="中国建筑作为一个独特的体系，到汉代已经确立。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%8B%AC%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%B0%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E7%A1%AE%E7%AB%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="木构架体系、院落式布局等特点已基本定型。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E5%BC%8F%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%AD%89%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%B7%B2%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9A%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="后期由于佛教哲学与艺术的传入，以及中国社会中玄学的兴起，建筑形象趋于雄浑而带巧丽的风格。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E7%8E%84%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B4%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E8%B6%8B%E4%BA%8E%E9%9B%84%E6%B5%91%E8%80%8C%E5%B8%A6%E5%B7%A7%E4%B8%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="东晋和南朝是我国自然式山水风景园林的奠基时期。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E6%99%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%9D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%BC%8F%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="四、封建社会中期（公元581~1279年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83581~1279%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="此阶段包括隋、唐、五代、宋、辽、金。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%9A%8B%E3%80%81%E5%94%90%E3%80%81%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%81%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%81%E8%BE%BD%E3%80%81%E9%87%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）隋（公元581~618年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E9%9A%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83581~618%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="隋代最突出的建筑成就就是新建一座都城一—大兴城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%80%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="隋文帝杨坚以汉长安城内宫殿与民居杂处，不便于民，水苦涩，不宜饮用为由，在汉长安的东南创建了一座全新的都城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E6%96%87%E5%B8%9D%E6%9D%A8%E5%9D%9A%E4%BB%A5%E6%B1%89%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E6%9D%82%E5%A4%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%B0%B4%E8%8B%A6%E6%B6%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%B1%89%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%97%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城的面积达84km2。城的外廓方正，城内有纵横干道各三条，称为“六街”。中轴线北端是宫城，宫城前是皇城。全城设108个坊和两伞市。每个坊都有坊墙围绕。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%BE%BE84km2%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%93%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E7%BA%B5%E6%A8%AA%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E5%90%84%E4%B8%89%E6%9D%A1%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%85%AD%E8%A1%97%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%8C%97%E7%AB%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E5%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9A%87%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E8%AE%BE108%E4%B8%AA%E5%9D%8A%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E5%9D%8A%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E5%9D%8A%E5%A2%99%E5%9B%B4%E7%BB%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城的东南隅曲江所在的低洼地段，辟为供居民游赏的园林，这在世界城市建设史上，都是值得称赞的举措。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%97%E9%9A%85%E6%9B%B2%E6%B1%9F%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8E%E6%B4%BC%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%9B%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%B8%B8%E8%B5%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E7%A7%B0%E8%B5%9E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BE%E6%8E%AA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="大兴城布局严整，街道平直，功能分区明确，规划设计得井井有条。这主要出自哲匠宇文恺之手。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%95%E4%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E6%9D%A1%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%93%B2%E5%8C%A0%E5%AE%87%E6%96%87%E6%81%BA%E4%B9%8B%E6%89%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宇文恺是一位杰出的建筑家，隋代的东都也是由他规划设计的。他考证" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%87%E6%96%87%E6%81%BA%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E6%9D%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E9%83%BD%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BB%96%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%E4%BB%96%E8%80%83%E8%AF%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="“明堂”，广引文献，并用1/100比例反制图、做模型。他还有许多具有巧思的建筑创作。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%82%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%BF%E5%BC%95%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E7%94%A81/100%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%E5%81%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%E4%BB%96%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%B7%A7%E6%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="隋代对佛教十分重视，隋文帝建国之初，曾诏令全国各州建“仁寿塔”，是方形平面五层的楼阁式木塔，可能有标准图，今塔已无一遗存。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%EF%BC%8C%E9%9A%8B%E6%96%87%E5%B8%9D%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%BE%E8%AF%8F%E4%BB%A4%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%84%E5%B7%9E%E5%BB%BA%E2%80%9C%E4%BB%81%E5%AF%BF%E5%A1%94%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E4%BA%94%E5%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%A8%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8A%E5%A1%94%E5%B7%B2%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%80%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="隋代遗存至今最著名的建筑是河北赵县的安济桥，是一座敞肩拱桥，它比欧洲同样类型的桥要早1200年。桥由28道石券并列而成，跨度达37.47m。“两涯嵌四穴，盖以杀怒水之激荡”。这种两端做成空腹拱的做法，不仅可减轻桥的自重，更可以减低洪水的冲击力。此桥在技术上，造型上都达到了很高的水平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E6%9C%80%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E8%B5%B5%E5%8E%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E6%B5%8E%E6%A1%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E6%95%9E%E8%82%A9%E6%8B%B1%E6%A1%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E6%AF%94%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B7%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%A1%A5%E8%A6%81%E6%97%A91200%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%82%E6%A1%A5%E7%94%B128%E9%81%93%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%B8%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%E8%80%8C%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%A8%E5%BA%A6%E8%BE%BE37.47m%E3%80%82%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%A4%E6%B6%AF%E5%B5%8C%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%96%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%80%E6%80%92%E6%B0%B4%E4%B9%8B%E6%BF%80%E8%8D%A1%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%A4%E7%AB%AF%E5%81%9A%E6%88%90%E7%A9%BA%E8%85%B9%E6%8B%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%87%8F%E8%BD%BB%E6%A1%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%87%8F%E4%BD%8E%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B2%E5%87%BB%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%82%E6%AD%A4%E6%A1%A5%E5%9C%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8A%E9%83%BD%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="桥的建造人是隋匠李春，这在中国一向不重视工匠的古代，能留下匠人的名字，是极难能可贵的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A1%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E9%9A%8B%E5%8C%A0%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8D%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%83%BD%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%9E%81%E9%9A%BE%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E8%B4%B5%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="隋代遗存的另一建筑是山东济南柳埠的神通寺四门塔，是一座平面为方形的单层石塔，建于隋大业七年（公元611年）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E6%B5%8E%E5%8D%97%E6%9F%B3%E5%9F%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A%E5%AF%BA%E5%9B%9B%E9%97%A8%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E5%B1%82%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%8E%E9%9A%8B%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%83%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83611%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）唐（公元618~907年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%94%90%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83618~907%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="唐代将隋代的大兴城改称长安城，作为都城，继续加以完善。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%86%E9%9A%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9%E7%A7%B0%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="后来因为宫殿不敷使用，在长安城东北隅城墙之外龙首原上修建了一座大明宫，大明宫逐渐成为唐代的政治中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%B7%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%9C%E5%8C%97%E9%9A%85%E5%9F%8E%E5%A2%99%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E9%BE%99%E9%A6%96%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%AB%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%AB%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="大明宫遗址已经考古发掘，其中的主要建筑含元殿、麟德殿等按遗址做了复原设计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%AB%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%90%AB%E5%85%83%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E9%BA%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%AE%BF%E7%AD%89%E6%8C%89%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%8D%E5%8E%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="大明宫的尺度比明清北京紫禁城的尺度要大得多，就是非主殿的麟德殿也是明清正殿太和殿面积的3倍。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%AF%94%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%BB%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%84%E9%BA%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%AE%BF%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%A3%E6%AE%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E6%AE%BF%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E7%9A%843%E5%80%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="唐代最宏伟的木构建筑当推武则天所建的“明堂”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%8F%E4%BC%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%93%E6%8E%A8%E6%AD%A6%E5%88%99%E5%A4%A9%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%82%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="文献记载它的平面为方形，约合98m见方，高约合86m，是一座底部为方形而顶部为圆形的三层楼阁。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A6%E5%90%8898m%E8%A7%81%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A6%E5%90%8886m%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%BA%95%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E8%80%8C%E9%A1%B6%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%86%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="建造如此复杂的高层建筑，工期只用10个月，由此可见当时的建筑设计与施工技术已臻于成熟。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A810%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E6%AD%A4%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%B7%B2%E8%87%BB%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E7%86%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="据近年对明堂遗址的考古发掘，其平面尺寸与结构同文献记载基本一致。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%B9%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%82%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E7%9A%84%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%90%8C%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="中国历史上曾有过多次“灭法”，即消灭宗教的活动，如著名的“三武一世”灭法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%BE%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E2%80%9C%E7%81%AD%E6%B3%95%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%B6%88%E7%81%AD%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%96%E2%80%9D%E7%81%AD%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="从北魏到五代，佛教建筑被拆毁殆尽，再加上木构建筑材料本身的不耐久，致使中国现存的木构佛殿很少有年代很早的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%86%E6%AF%81%E6%AE%86%E5%B0%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%90%E4%B9%85%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%B4%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%9B%E6%AE%BF%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BE%88%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="最早的一座是山西五台的南禅寺大殿（唐建中三年、公元782年）。建于唐大中十一年（公元857年）的佛光寺东大殿是唐代会昌灭法以后所建。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%97%E7%A6%85%E5%AF%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%94%90%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83782%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%94%90%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83857%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E6%98%AF%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E4%BC%9A%E6%98%8C%E7%81%AD%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="佛光寺东大殿是现存唐代木构建筑中规模最大，质量最好的一座，但以之与敦煌壁画上所绘的唐代佛寺中殿阁楼台恢宏的建筑群相比，仍不免简约。不过仅就佛光寺东大殿来看，其结构的有机、木构件的雄劲，已能让人领会到唐代木构建筑所达到的高水平。它的木构用料已具模数、斗棋功能分明，尤其是脊模之下只用大叉手而不施侏儒柱，表明唐代匠人已经了解三角形为稳定形的原理。它的屋顶平缓、出檐深远，造型庄重美观，建筑技术与艺术达到了和谐统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%BB%A5%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%A6%E7%85%8C%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%80%E7%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%AD%E6%AE%BF%E9%98%81%E6%A5%BC%E5%8F%B0%E6%81%A2%E5%AE%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%8D%E7%AE%80%E7%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E4%B8%8D%E8%BF%87%E4%BB%85%E5%B0%B1%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E6%9D%A5%E7%9C%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%84%E5%8A%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E9%A2%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%89%80%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E7%94%A8%E6%96%99%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%B7%E6%A8%A1%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E6%98%AF%E8%84%8A%E6%A8%A1%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%89%E6%89%8B%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%BD%E4%BE%8F%E5%84%92%E6%9F%B1%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%BA%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%B9%B3%E7%BC%93%E3%80%81%E5%87%BA%E6%AA%90%E6%B7%B1%E8%BF%9C%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E5%BA%84%E9%87%8D%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="唐代的木塔无一幸存到今天，砖塔则尚有数座，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E5%A1%94%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B8%E5%AD%98%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%E5%88%99%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%95%B0%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如西安大慈恩寺的大雁塔、长安区的兴教寺玄奘墓塔，这两座塔属于楼阁式塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%85%88%E6%81%A9%E5%AF%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%81%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B4%E6%95%99%E5%AF%BA%E7%8E%84%E5%A5%98%E5%A2%93%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E5%BA%A7%E5%A1%94%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="西安荐福寺小雁塔、河南登封法王寺塔和云南大理崇圣寺千寻塔，三者属于密檐式塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%89%E8%8D%90%E7%A6%8F%E5%AF%BA%E5%B0%8F%E9%9B%81%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%81%E6%B3%95%E7%8E%8B%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%A7%E7%90%86%E5%B4%87%E5%9C%A3%E5%AF%BA%E5%8D%83%E5%AF%BB%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%89%E8%80%85%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%AF%86%E6%AA%90%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="唐代的单层塔多属于高僧的墓塔，如河南登封净藏禅师塔、山西平顺海会院明惠大师塔等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E5%A4%9A%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%83%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%93%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%81%E5%87%80%E8%97%8F%E7%A6%85%E5%B8%88%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%B9%B3%E9%A1%BA%E6%B5%B7%E4%BC%9A%E9%99%A2%E6%98%8E%E6%83%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E5%A1%94%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="唐塔一般是方形平面，单层塔壁，以木楼板木扶梯分层。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E5%A1%94%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%98%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%95%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E5%A3%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%A8%E6%A5%BC%E6%9D%BF%E6%9C%A8%E6%89%B6%E6%A2%AF%E5%88%86%E5%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="净藏禅师塔是八角形平面，是已知唐塔中用八角形平面的首例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%87%80%E8%97%8F%E7%A6%85%E5%B8%88%E5%A1%94%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AB%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E5%94%90%E5%A1%94%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AB%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="唐代帝陵的特点是“因山为穴”。18座唐陵中有16座是利用天然山体凿隧道修筑的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%B8%9D%E9%99%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%A0%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%BA%E7%A9%B4%E2%80%9D%E3%80%8218%E5%BA%A7%E5%94%90%E9%99%B5%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%8916%E5%BA%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E5%B1%B1%E4%BD%93%E5%87%BF%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E4%BF%AE%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="以唐高宗李治与武则天的乾陵为例，以阙及神道形成前导空间，在建筑布局上有显著进步。每座陵都有若干陪葬墓。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E5%94%90%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%97%E6%9D%8E%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%8E%E6%AD%A6%E5%88%99%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%BE%E9%99%B5%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%99%E5%8F%8A%E7%A5%9E%E9%81%93%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%89%8D%E5%AF%BC%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8F%E5%BA%A7%E9%99%B5%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E9%99%AA%E8%91%AC%E5%A2%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="经考古发掘的永泰公主墓等若干陪葬墓中的壁画、明器等为了解唐代宫廷生活与唐代建筑形象提供了珍贵资特。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%8F%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%B0%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%A2%93%E7%AD%89%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E9%99%AA%E8%91%AC%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E3%80%81%E6%98%8E%E5%99%A8%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%AB%E5%BB%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%8E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86%E7%8F%8D%E8%B4%B5%E8%B5%84%E7%89%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="唐代对各等级住宅的堂、舍、门屋的间数、架数、屋顶形式以及装饰等，均有制度规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%AF%B9%E5%90%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E8%88%8D%E3%80%81%E9%97%A8%E5%B1%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E6%9E%B6%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="盛唐时，显贵住宅趋于奢丽。安史之乱后，长安有些豪宅修建过度，规模庞大，装修华丽，使用高级木料，一时号为“木妖”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9B%9B%E5%94%90%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E8%B4%B5%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E8%B6%8B%E4%BA%8E%E5%A5%A2%E4%B8%BD%E3%80%82%E5%AE%89%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%8B%E4%B9%B1%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%9B%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%BA%9E%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E6%9C%A8%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%A8%E5%A6%96%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）五代（公元907~960年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83907~960%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="这又是一个多战乱的时代我方尤甚。相对地说南方的吴越、前蜀、南汉等较为稳定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%88%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%9A%E6%88%98%E4%B9%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E6%88%91%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%A4%E7%94%9A%E3%80%82%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%9C%B0%E8%AF%B4%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%90%B4%E8%B6%8A%E3%80%81%E5%89%8D%E8%9C%80%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E6%B1%89%E7%AD%89%E8%BE%83%E4%B8%BA%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此时期重要的建筑遗物如：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%81%97%E7%89%A9%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="苏州虎丘的云岩寺塔。该塔原为9层，现存7层，是一座八角形平面，双层塔壁的砖塔。它是砖塔由唐代的方形平面单层塔壁，向宋塔的多边形平面、有塔心室转变的首例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8B%8F%E5%B7%9E%E8%99%8E%E4%B8%98%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%91%E5%B2%A9%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%E8%AF%A5%E5%A1%94%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%BA9%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%987%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%85%AB%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E5%A3%81%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%E5%AE%83%E6%98%AF%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%E7%94%B1%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%8D%95%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E5%A3%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%91%E5%AE%8B%E5%A1%94%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E8%BE%B9%E5%BD%A2%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E5%A1%94%E5%BF%83%E5%AE%A4%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="南京栖霞山舍利塔也是此时期的遗物。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%A0%96%E9%9C%9E%E5%B1%B1%E8%88%8D%E5%88%A9%E5%A1%94%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%81%97%E7%89%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="前蜀王建墓位于成都近郊，是中国属于王一级的墓最早被正式考古发掘的，在建筑史上有一定价值，墓中棺床的石刻较著名。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%89%8D%E8%9C%80%E7%8E%8B%E5%BB%BA%E5%A2%93%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E8%BF%91%E9%83%8A%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%93%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E8%A2%AB%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E8%80%83%E5%8F%A4%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%98%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%A3%BA%E5%BA%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%BB%E8%BE%83%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）宋（公元960~1279年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83960~1279%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋代建都汴梁，即今开封，汴梁原为州治所在，作为国都过于狭隘。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%BA%E5%B7%9E%E6%B2%BB%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%8E%E7%8B%AD%E9%9A%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="再加上宋代手工业商业活跃繁荣，自古以来的城市里坊制度被突破，拆除坊墙，临街设市肆，沿巷建住房，形成开放性城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%B4%BB%E8%B7%83%E7%B9%81%E8%8D%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%87%8C%E5%9D%8A%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%E5%9D%8A%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%B4%E8%A1%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%B8%82%E8%82%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%BF%E5%B7%B7%E5%BB%BA%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="这是中国城市史上一个重要的转折点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%AC%E6%8A%98%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋代的建筑风格趋向于精致绮丽，屋顶形式丰富多样，装修细巧，门、窗、勾阑等根格花样很多。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E8%B6%8B%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8E%E7%B2%BE%E8%87%B4%E7%BB%AE%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E7%BB%86%E5%B7%A7%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E7%AA%97%E3%80%81%E5%8B%BE%E9%98%91%E7%AD%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%A0%BC%E8%8A%B1%E6%A0%B7%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="留存至今的木构殿堂尚有不少，常以山西太原晋祠圣母殿（宋天圣年间初建，崇宁元年重建）和河北正定隆兴寺摩尼殿（宋皇祐四年即公元1052年建）为宋代建筑的代表作。其实，它们尚不能充分地表现出宋代建筑的风格与实际达到的水平。可以从宋代的“界画”上看到宋代的重楼飞阁是如何的华丽繁复。汴梁地处南北两种建筑风格之间，同时受北方唐代的壮硕与南方五代秀丽风格的影响，形成了宋代建筑的风格。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%95%99%E5%AD%98%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%AE%BF%E5%A0%82%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%8E%9F%E6%99%8B%E7%A5%A0%E5%9C%A3%E6%AF%8D%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%8B%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%A3%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%B4%E5%88%9D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%B4%87%E5%AE%81%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%9A%E9%9A%86%E5%85%B4%E5%AF%BA%E6%91%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%8B%E7%9A%87%E7%A5%90%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831052%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E5%B0%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BB%8E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E7%95%8C%E7%94%BB%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E6%A5%BC%E9%A3%9E%E9%98%81%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BD%E7%B9%81%E5%A4%8D%E3%80%82%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%84%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%97%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AE%E7%A1%95%E4%B8%8E%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E7%A7%80%E4%B8%BD%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋塔遗存至今的尚有许多，有砖塔、石塔还有琉璃贴面的琉璃塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E5%A1%94%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E8%B4%B4%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如：河北定县开元寺料敌塔，是现存最高的砖塔，高84m。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%8E%BF%E5%BC%80%E5%85%83%E5%AF%BA%E6%96%99%E6%95%8C%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%9884m%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="河南开封祐国寺塔，俗称铁塔，是第一座砌琉璃面砖的塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%E7%A5%90%E5%9B%BD%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E9%93%81%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E7%A0%8C%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E9%9D%A2%E7%A0%96%E7%9A%84%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="福建泉州开元寺双石塔，是现存最高的石塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E6%B3%89%E5%B7%9E%E5%BC%80%E5%85%83%E5%AF%BA%E5%8F%8C%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="宋崇宁二年（公元1103年）颁布的《营造法式》，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E5%B4%87%E5%AE%81%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831103%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%A2%81%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="内容包括了“以材为祖”的木作做法及各工种的功限料例，附有图样。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%90%E4%B8%BA%E7%A5%96%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A7%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E9%99%90%E6%96%99%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%84%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="全书共34卷，是一部极有价值的术书，作者是宋代的将作监李诫。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%A8%E4%B9%A6%E5%85%B134%E5%8D%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%83%A8%E6%9E%81%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AF%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%86%E4%BD%9C%E7%9B%91%E6%9D%8E%E8%AF%AB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="李诫字明仲，河南管城县人。李诫是很有学问的人，他广读文献，并深入工匠做了解，写成此书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9D%8E%E8%AF%AB%E5%AD%97%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%AE%A1%E5%9F%8E%E5%8E%BF%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%E6%9D%8E%E8%AF%AB%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%88%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%A6%E9%97%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E5%B9%BF%E8%AF%BB%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%99%E6%88%90%E6%AD%A4%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="据传他参考的书中有一本《木经》是五代哲匠喻皓所著。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8D%AE%E4%BC%A0%E4%BB%96%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%8A%E6%9C%A8%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E5%93%B2%E5%8C%A0%E5%96%BB%E7%9A%93%E6%89%80%E8%91%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="自南北朝时胡床、交椅等高足坐具传入中原以来，室内家具日渐多样，桌椅等垂足坐家具逐渐取代了供跪坐的几案等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%87%AA%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E6%97%B6%E8%83%A1%E5%BA%8A%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%A4%85%E7%AD%89%E9%AB%98%E8%B6%B3%E5%9D%90%E5%85%B7%E4%BC%A0%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%90%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%A1%8C%E6%A4%85%E7%AD%89%E5%9E%82%E8%B6%B3%E5%9D%90%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%BA%86%E4%BE%9B%E8%B7%AA%E5%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E6%A1%88%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="从五代《韩熙载夜宴图》上可见一斑。至宋代，垂足坐家具已基本普及，这影响建筑的室内高度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8A%E9%9F%A9%E7%86%99%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%9C%E5%AE%B4%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%E4%B8%80%E6%96%91%E3%80%82%E8%87%B3%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%9E%82%E8%B6%B3%E5%9D%90%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E5%B7%B2%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%8A%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="宋代的造园之风甚炽，从宫廷、州县公署到市肆和一般士庶，都热衷于造园。宋徽宗的“艮岳”更成为亡宋的导火线。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E4%B9%8B%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%9A%E7%82%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E5%AE%AB%E5%BB%B7%E3%80%81%E5%B7%9E%E5%8E%BF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0%E5%B8%82%E8%82%86%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E7%83%AD%E8%A1%B7%E4%BA%8E%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E3%80%82%E5%AE%8B%E5%BE%BD%E5%AE%97%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E8%89%AE%E5%B2%B3%E2%80%9D%E6%9B%B4%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%A1%E5%AE%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%BC%E7%81%AB%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="南宋定都临安，即今杭州。建筑规模不大，但精致，属南方风格，多采用穿斗架，即使是官方所建寺观，也具南方地方风格。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%97%E5%AE%8B%E5%AE%9A%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%B4%E5%AE%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BB%8A%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E3%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E7%B2%BE%E8%87%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%9E%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BF%E6%96%97%E6%9E%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%BF%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E5%AF%BA%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%85%B7%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）辽（公元907~1125年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E8%BE%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83907~1125%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="辽是由北方契丹族统治的朝代，与北宋对峙。辽的统治者积极吸取汉族文化，辽代建筑可视为唐代建筑的延续。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BE%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%A5%91%E4%B8%B9%E6%97%8F%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%8B%E5%AF%B9%E5%B3%99%E3%80%82%E8%BE%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E7%A7%AF%E6%9E%81%E5%90%B8%E5%8F%96%E6%B1%89%E6%97%8F%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%B6%E7%BB%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="辽代遗留至今的两处最著名的古建筑，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BE%BD%E4%BB%A3%E9%81%97%E7%95%99%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%84%E6%9C%80%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一处是天津蓟县独乐寺的山门和观音阁（公元984年），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E8%93%9F%E5%8E%BF%E7%8B%AC%E4%B9%90%E5%AF%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%B1%E9%97%A8%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E9%98%81%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83984%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另一处是山西应县佛宫寺释迦塔（公元1056年）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%BA%94%E5%8E%BF%E4%BD%9B%E5%AE%AB%E5%AF%BA%E9%87%8A%E8%BF%A6%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831056%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="前者是现存最大的木构楼阁的精品，后者是现存年代最早而且是独一无二的楼阁式木塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%89%8D%E8%80%85%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E7%9A%84%E7%B2%BE%E5%93%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E8%80%85%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E6%98%AF%E7%8B%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%A8%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="观音阁外观二层，内部三层，中间有一夹层。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E9%98%81%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%E4%BA%8C%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%B9%E5%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="释迦塔俗名应县木塔，塔高67.31m，斗棋式样有60余种，外观5层，有四个夹层，实为9层，夹层中均有斜撑构件，结构合乎力学原理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%8A%E8%BF%A6%E5%A1%94%E4%BF%97%E5%90%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%8E%BF%E6%9C%A8%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%94%E9%AB%9867.31m%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E5%BC%8F%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%8960%E4%BD%99%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%825%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%B9%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA9%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%B9%E5%B1%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%89%E6%96%9C%E6%92%91%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%90%88%E4%B9%8E%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="由辽代这两座木构建筑的技术与艺术所达到的水平，可以反过来推断唐及北宋中原地区木构建筑达到了何等的高水平" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E8%BE%BD%E4%BB%A3%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E5%BA%A7%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%89%80%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8D%E8%BF%87%E6%9D%A5%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%AD%E5%94%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%BD%95%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（六）金（公元1115~1234年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E9%87%91%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831115~1234%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="金破宋都汴梁时，拆迁若干宫殿苑囿中的建筑及太湖石等至中都，并带去图书、文物及工匠等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%AE%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%86%E8%BF%81%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E8%8B%91%E5%9B%BF%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%AA%E6%B9%96%E7%9F%B3%E7%AD%89%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E5%8E%BB%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在中都兴建的宫殿被称为“工巧无遗力，所谓穷奢极侈者”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%BD%E5%85%B4%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E8%A2%AB%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E5%B7%A7%E6%97%A0%E9%81%97%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E8%B0%93%E7%A9%B7%E5%A5%A2%E6%9E%81%E4%BE%88%E8%80%85%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宫殿用彩色琉璃瓦屋面，红色墙垣，白色汉白玉华表、石阶、栏杆，色彩浓郁亮丽，开中国建筑用色强烈之始。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E7%93%A6%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E5%A2%99%E5%9E%A3%EF%BC%8C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E6%B1%89%E7%99%BD%E7%8E%89%E5%8D%8E%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E9%98%B6%E3%80%81%E6%A0%8F%E6%9D%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E6%B5%93%E9%83%81%E4%BA%AE%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%94%A8%E8%89%B2%E5%BC%BA%E7%83%88%E4%B9%8B%E5%A7%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="金代的地方建筑中用减柱造、移柱造之风盛行，被认为“制度不经”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%91%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%87%8F%E6%9F%B1%E9%80%A0%E3%80%81%E7%A7%BB%E6%9F%B1%E9%80%A0%E4%B9%8B%E9%A3%8E%E7%9B%9B%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%A2%AB%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%BB%8F%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如五台山佛光寺文殊殿，内柱仅留两根，是减柱造极端之例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E6%96%87%E6%AE%8A%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E6%9F%B1%E4%BB%85%E7%95%99%E4%B8%A4%E6%A0%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%87%8F%E6%9F%B1%E9%80%A0%E6%9E%81%E7%AB%AF%E4%B9%8B%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="北京西郊的卢沟桥，长265m，是金代所建的一座联拱石桥。桥栏望柱头上的石狮子极多，以数不清到底有多少而著称。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A2%E6%B2%9F%E6%A1%A5%EF%BC%8C%E9%95%BF265m%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E9%87%91%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%81%94%E6%8B%B1%E7%9F%B3%E6%A1%A5%E3%80%82%E6%A1%A5%E6%A0%8F%E6%9C%9B%E6%9F%B1%E5%A4%B4%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E8%80%8C%E8%91%97%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="综观此阶段历时700余年，以唐代为高潮。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BC%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8E%86%E6%97%B6700%E4%BD%99%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="长安城规模之大，列为人类进入资本主义社会之前城市中的世界第一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E8%B5%84%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这时期遗留下来的陵墓、木构佛殿、石窟寺、塔、桥及城市宫殿遗址，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E9%81%97%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E3%80%81%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%9B%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%81%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E6%A1%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在布局上、造型上都是气概雄伟、技术与艺术均有很高水平，建筑物中的雕塑、壁画尤为精美。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%81%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8A%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%B0%94%E6%A6%82%E9%9B%84%E4%BC%9F%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%95%E5%A1%91%E3%80%81%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E5%B0%A4%E4%B8%BA%E7%B2%BE%E7%BE%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="唐代是中国建筑发展的最高峰，唐代的大建筑群布局舒展，前导空间流畅，个体建筑结构合理有机，斗棋雄劲。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E8%88%92%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%8D%E5%AF%BC%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%B5%81%E7%95%85%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E9%9B%84%E5%8A%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑风格明朗、雄健、伟丽。本阶段中国建筑体系达到成熟。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%97%E3%80%81%E9%9B%84%E5%81%A5%E3%80%81%E4%BC%9F%E4%B8%BD%E3%80%82%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%88%90%E7%86%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="五、封建社会后期（公元1279~1911年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831279~1911%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="此阶段包括元、明、清。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%83%E3%80%81%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）元（公元1279~1368年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%85%83%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831279~1368%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元代是由蒙古族统治的朝代，是中国由少数民族建立的列入正统的第一个统一的大帝国。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E6%97%8F%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B1%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B0%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E6%AD%A3%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此前的各少数民族建立的国家只是局部的地方政权。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B0%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%94%BF%E6%9D%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元代在建筑上最重大的成就是完全新建了一座都城——大都。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元大都基本上符合《周礼·考工记》中所述的“王城之制”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E8%BF%B0%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%B6%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="它位于金中都的东北方，城的外廓近于方形，除北面开二门外，其余三面都是开三门。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E9%87%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%93%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A4%E5%8C%97%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E4%BA%8C%E9%97%A8%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BD%99%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%A2%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%89%E9%97%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宫城靠南，宫城以北是漕运终点的商业区，太庙在东侧，社稷坛在西侧，布局上基本符合“方九里，旁三门……面朝后市、左祖右社”的规矩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E9%9D%A0%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8C%97%E6%98%AF%E6%BC%95%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%88%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%AA%E5%BA%99%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%9C%E4%BE%A7%EF%BC%8C%E7%A4%BE%E7%A8%B7%E5%9D%9B%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%BE%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E2%80%9C%E6%96%B9%E4%B9%9D%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%81%E4%B8%89%E9%97%A8%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A6%E7%A5%96%E5%8F%B3%E7%A4%BE%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E7%9F%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="大都的街道取棋盘状，在南北走向的干道之间平行排列着称为“胡同”的小巷，是成排四合院住宅院落之间的通道。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E5%8F%96%E6%A3%8B%E7%9B%98%E7%8A%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E7%9D%80%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E8%83%A1%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%88%90%E6%8E%92%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%88%E9%99%A2%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="元大都是一座规划周密的城市，街道平直，市政工程完备，郭守敬引西山和昌平水源解决了酒运问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%91%A8%E5%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%8C%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%AD%E5%AE%88%E6%95%AC%E5%BC%95%E8%A5%BF%E5%B1%B1%E5%92%8C%E6%98%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E4%BA%86%E9%85%92%E8%BF%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="元大都的规划设计人有刘秉忠和阿拉伯人也黑迭耳。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%88%98%E7%A7%89%E5%BF%A0%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E9%BB%91%E8%BF%AD%E8%80%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="元代的宫殿多用工字殿，这是继承宋代传统。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="元代宫殿的特色是使用多彩琉璃、高级木料紫檀、金色红色装饰，壁上挂毛或丝制品的帐幕等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E5%BD%A9%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E6%9C%A8%E6%96%99%E7%B4%AB%E6%AA%80%E3%80%81%E9%87%91%E8%89%B2%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%81%E4%B8%8A%E6%8C%82%E6%AF%9B%E6%88%96%E4%B8%9D%E5%88%B6%E5%93%81%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%90%E5%B9%95%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宫殿中出现孟顶殿、棕毛殿、畏吾儿殿、石造浴室、石皮藏室等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%9F%E9%A1%B6%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E6%A3%95%E6%AF%9B%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E7%95%8F%E5%90%BE%E5%84%BF%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E9%80%A0%E6%B5%B4%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E7%9A%AE%E8%97%8F%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="元代的木构建筑趋于简化，用料及加工都较粗放。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%B6%8B%E4%BA%8E%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E6%96%99%E5%8F%8A%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%BD%E8%BE%83%E7%B2%97%E6%94%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="主要表现是斗棋缩小，柱与梁直接联络，多做彻上明造，减柱仍在采用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E6%98%AF%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E7%BC%A9%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%B1%E4%B8%8E%E6%A2%81%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%81%94%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%81%9A%E5%BD%BB%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%8E%E9%80%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E6%9F%B1%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="通常以山西洪洞县广胜寺下寺正殿作为元代建筑的代表作。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E6%B4%AA%E6%B4%9E%E5%8E%BF%E5%B9%BF%E8%83%9C%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%8B%E5%AF%BA%E6%AD%A3%E6%AE%BF%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="山西芮城的道观永乐宫是元初的建筑，以内中的壁画著称。永乐宫原址在山西永济，因修三门峡水库而移建芮城，是我国文物保护迁建古建筑较成功的一例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E8%8A%AE%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%A7%82%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%90%E5%AE%AB%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E5%88%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%86%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E8%91%97%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%90%E5%AE%AB%E5%8E%9F%E5%9D%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E6%B0%B8%E6%B5%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%BF%AE%E4%B8%89%E9%97%A8%E5%B3%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%93%E8%80%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%BB%BA%E8%8A%AE%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%BF%81%E5%BB%BA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%BE%83%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="元代引进了若干新的建筑类型，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%9B%E4%BA%86%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如大都中的大圣寿方安寺（妙应寺）白塔，是一座覆钵式塔（喇嘛塔），是尼泊尔匠人阿尼哥所建。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%A3%E5%AF%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%89%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%99%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%89%E7%99%BD%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%A6%86%E9%92%B5%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%BC%E6%B3%8A%E5%B0%94%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%BC%E5%93%A5%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在河南登封有一座由郭守敬建造的观星台，是中国最早的一座天文台。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E7%94%B1%E9%83%AD%E5%AE%88%E6%95%AC%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%82%E6%98%9F%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="居庸关云台原是座过街塔的塔座，上面原有三座覆体式塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E5%BA%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%91%E5%8F%B0%E5%8E%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%BA%A7%E8%BF%87%E8%A1%97%E5%A1%94%E7%9A%84%E5%A1%94%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E8%A6%86%E4%BD%93%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="元代的戏曲极盛行，元曲与唐诗、宋词并称，与之相应的戏台建筑很多，至今在山西临汾等多处仍有元代戏台留存。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%88%8F%E6%9B%B2%E6%9E%81%E7%9B%9B%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E6%9B%B2%E4%B8%8E%E5%94%90%E8%AF%97%E3%80%81%E5%AE%8B%E8%AF%8D%E5%B9%B6%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%B9%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E6%88%8F%E5%8F%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%B4%E6%B1%BE%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%84%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E6%88%8F%E5%8F%B0%E7%95%99%E5%AD%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）明（公元1368~1644年" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831368~1644%E5%B9%B4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明代曾在南京、临濠（凤阳北京先后三次建造都城和宫殿，建设经验丰富，有一批熟练的工官与工匠。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B4%E6%BF%A0%EF%BC%88%E5%87%A4%E9%98%B3%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%85%88%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%A1%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E6%89%B9%E7%86%9F%E7%BB%83%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="明成祖在元大都的基址上建设北京城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E6%88%90%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%9D%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在用砖砌元大都的土城时，去掉了北边不发达的五里，向南边扩展一里。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E7%94%A8%E7%A0%96%E7%A0%8C%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9F%8E%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%89%E4%BA%86%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%91%E8%BE%BE%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%91%E5%8D%97%E8%BE%B9%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%80%E9%87%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="到嘉靖年间加建外城时，从南郊开始，中途收口，形成了北京城特有的凸字形外轮廓。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%B0%E5%98%89%E9%9D%96%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%96%E5%9F%8E%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E5%8D%97%E9%83%8A%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%94%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%87%B8%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E5%A4%96%E8%BD%AE%E5%BB%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="北京城有一条从南到北约长7.5公里的中轴线。中轴线通过紫禁城，最重要的建筑都位于这条中轴线上。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%8E%E5%8D%97%E5%88%B0%E5%8C%97%E7%BA%A6%E9%95%BF7.5%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%83%BD%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E8%BF%99%E6%9D%A1%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="紫禁城宫殿规划设计严整，造型壮丽，功能完备，是院落式建筑群的最高典范。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E5%A3%AE%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%8C%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%85%B8%E8%8C%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明代在北京还建造了各种坛庙：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%BF%98%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%9D%9B%E5%BA%99%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="如：太庙、社稷、天、地、日、月、先农、先蚕等坛。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%AA%E5%BA%99%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E7%A8%B7%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E3%80%81%E6%9C%88%E3%80%81%E5%85%88%E5%86%9C%E3%80%81%E5%85%88%E8%9A%95%E7%AD%89%E5%9D%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="并修建了衙署、仓扇、寺观、府邸等。重要建筑均采用楠木，规模及造型严谨规整。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B6%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%A1%99%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%81%E4%BB%93%E6%89%87%E3%80%81%E5%AF%BA%E8%A7%82%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9C%E9%82%B8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9D%87%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%A5%A0%E6%9C%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%8F%8A%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%A5%E8%B0%A8%E8%A7%84%E6%95%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="明代的13座陵墓位于昌平天寿山麓。它的地形选择和神道等前导空间的处理都很成功。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%8413%E5%BA%A7%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%A4%A9%E5%AF%BF%E5%B1%B1%E9%BA%93%E3%80%82%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%92%8C%E7%A5%9E%E9%81%93%E7%AD%89%E5%89%8D%E5%AF%BC%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E9%83%BD%E5%BE%88%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="明长陵的凌恩殿木构架中的12根金丝楠木柱，柱高约23m，最大柱径达1.17m，蔚为壮观。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E9%95%BF%E9%99%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%87%8C%E6%81%A9%E6%AE%BF%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%8412%E6%A0%B9%E9%87%91%E4%B8%9D%E6%A5%A0%E6%9C%A8%E6%9F%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A623m%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%9F%B1%E5%BE%84%E8%BE%BE1.17m%EF%BC%8C%E8%94%9A%E4%B8%BA%E5%A3%AE%E8%A7%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="明代制砖的数量与质量均有很大提高，不仅把大都的土墙改为砖餮，万里长城以及许多州、府、县的砖城墙也多是明代所建。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%88%B6%E7%A0%96%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E6%8A%8A%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%A2%99%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%96%E9%A4%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%87%E9%87%8C%E9%95%BF%E5%9F%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E5%B7%9E%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9C%E3%80%81%E5%8E%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%96%E5%9F%8E%E5%A2%99%E4%B9%9F%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="砌砖技术的大发展，出现了完全不用木料，以砖拱券为结构的无梁殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A0%8C%E7%A0%96%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%A8%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%A0%96%E6%8B%B1%E5%88%B8%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E6%A2%81%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="最著名的一处是南京灵谷寺的无量殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%80%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%81%B5%E8%B0%B7%E5%AF%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E9%87%8F%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明代的琉璃制品也达到了极高水平，色彩及纹饰丰富。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E5%88%B6%E5%93%81%E4%B9%9F%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%9E%81%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E5%8F%8A%E7%BA%B9%E9%A5%B0%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="南京报恩寺塔，高80余米，塔身遍饰有佛像、力士、飞天等纹饰的彩色琉璃砖，绚丽壮观，被列为当时世界七大建筑奇迹之一，可惜在太平天国时被毁。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%A5%E6%81%A9%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%9880%E4%BD%99%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%94%E8%BA%AB%E9%81%8D%E9%A5%B0%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%9B%E5%83%8F%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9B%E5%A3%AB%E3%80%81%E9%A3%9E%E5%A4%A9%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%B9%E9%A5%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A9%E8%89%B2%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E7%A0%96%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9A%E4%B8%BD%E5%A3%AE%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%97%E4%B8%BA%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A5%87%E8%BF%B9%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%83%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="山西大同的九龙壁和山西洪洞广胜寺上寺飞虹塔也是明代的琉璃建筑，可以略见明代琉璃的风采。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%99%E5%A3%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E6%B4%AA%E6%B4%9E%E5%B9%BF%E8%83%9C%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%AF%BA%E9%A3%9E%E8%99%B9%E5%A1%94%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%95%A5%E8%A7%81%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%87%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="在明代，中国佛塔增加一种类型，即在北京大正（真）觉寺仿印度佛陀伽耶大塔建造的一座金刚宝座式塔。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BD%9B%E5%A1%94%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A3%EF%BC%88%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%BB%BF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%BD%9B%E9%99%80%E4%BC%BD%E8%80%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%A1%94%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E5%AE%9D%E5%BA%A7%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明代家具用花梨、紫檀等质地坚实的名贵木料，构件断面小，椎卯严紧密实，不多加装饰，造型与受力情况和谐一致。美观高雅，明式家具驰誉世界。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E7%94%A8%E8%8A%B1%E6%A2%A8%E3%80%81%E7%B4%AB%E6%AA%80%E7%AD%89%E8%B4%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%9A%E5%AE%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E8%B4%B5%E6%9C%A8%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%A4%8E%E5%8D%AF%E4%B8%A5%E7%B4%A7%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%9E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%A0%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%97%E5%8A%9B%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E3%80%82%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E9%A9%B0%E8%AA%89%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明初朱元璋曾明令禁止宅旁多留隙地营造花园，但明中叶后，江南富庶之地，私家造园之风甚炽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%83%E7%92%8B%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A4%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E5%AE%85%E6%97%81%E5%A4%9A%E7%95%99%E9%9A%99%E5%9C%B0%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E8%8A%B1%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B6%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E5%AF%8C%E5%BA%B6%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E4%B9%8B%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%9A%E7%82%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明末吴江人计成著有《园冶》一书，记述反映了明代造园理论与艺术水平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%AB%E5%90%B4%E6%B1%9F%E4%BA%BA%E8%AE%A1%E6%88%90%E8%91%97%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8A%E5%9B%AD%E5%86%B6%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明代修建北京宫殿、坛庙、陵墓的工匠来自全国各地，其中主力来自江南，以徐呆、蒯祥最为杰出。蒯祥能“目量意营”，“随手图之无不称上意”，人称“蒯鲁班”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%9D%9B%E5%BA%99%E3%80%81%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%9B%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%90%E5%91%86%E3%80%81%E8%92%AF%E7%A5%A5%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%BA%E6%9D%B0%E5%87%BA%E3%80%82%E8%92%AF%E7%A5%A5%E8%83%BD%E2%80%9C%E7%9B%AE%E9%87%8F%E6%84%8F%E8%90%A5%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E9%9A%8F%E6%89%8B%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%8A%E6%84%8F%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E8%92%AF%E9%B2%81%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）清（公元1644~1911年）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831644~1911%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="清代定都北京，没有沿用过去每改朝换代均要焚毁前朝宫室以煞王气的传统，继续使用了明代的紫禁城，在使用中加以完善。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%B2%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB%E6%AF%8F%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%9D%E6%8D%A2%E4%BB%A3%E5%9D%87%E8%A6%81%E7%84%9A%E6%AF%81%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9D%E5%AE%AB%E5%AE%A4%E4%BB%A5%E7%85%9E%E7%8E%8B%E6%B0%94%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="清代在建筑方面最突出的成就表现在皇家苑囿的建设上。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%80%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%91%E5%9B%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="除了在北京城内的三海多有建树之外，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%91%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在西郊所建的三山五园和在承德所建的避暑山庄都达到了很高的水平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%8A%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%B1%E4%BA%94%E5%9B%AD%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%BF%E5%BE%B7%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%81%BF%E6%9A%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%BA%84%E9%83%BD%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="私家园林也大有发展，江南园林达到极盛。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E4%B9%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%9E%81%E7%9B%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国园林影响所及，不仅是近邻的日本、朝鲜，18世纪时更远及欧洲。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%89%80%E5%8F%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%91%E9%82%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%81%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%EF%BC%8C18%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9B%B4%E8%BF%9C%E5%8F%8A%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国园林成为世界园林渊源之一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E6%B8%8A%E6%BA%90%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="清代为满族统治的朝代，为了团结蒙、藏兄弟民族，在西藏、青海、甘肃、蒙古等地修建了若干喇嘛庙。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%BA%E6%BB%A1%E6%97%8F%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%A2%E7%BB%93%E8%92%99%E3%80%81%E8%97%8F%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%E6%B5%B7%E3%80%81%E7%94%98%E8%82%83%E3%80%81%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E5%BA%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="清初在拉萨修建的布达拉宫，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E5%88%9D%E5%9C%A8%E6%8B%89%E8%90%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%BE%E6%8B%89%E5%AE%AB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在呼和浩特修建的席力图召，都是汉藏混合式的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%91%BC%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%A9%E7%89%B9%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%AD%E5%8A%9B%E5%9B%BE%E5%8F%AC%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%B1%89%E8%97%8F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在承德避暑山庄周围修建的“外八庙”结合山坡地形，仿建布达拉宫等建筑，融合了汉藏两式建筑而有所创新，使中国建筑有了一个新的发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%BF%E5%BE%B7%E9%81%BF%E6%9A%91%E5%B1%B1%E5%BA%84%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%96%E5%85%AB%E5%BA%99%E2%80%9D%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%BE%E6%8B%89%E5%AE%AB%E7%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%9E%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BA%86%E6%B1%89%E8%97%8F%E4%B8%A4%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="清代于雍正十二年（公元1734年）颁布了工部《工程做法则例》，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E4%BA%8E%E9%9B%8D%E6%AD%A3%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831734%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%A2%81%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%88%99%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="列出了27种单体官式建筑的各种构件的尺寸。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%97%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8627%E7%A7%8D%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%93%E5%AE%98%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="改宋式的以“材”、“架”为模数的方法为以“斗口”为模数，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%94%B9%E5%AE%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E6%9D%90%E2%80%9D%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E6%9E%B6%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E6%96%97%E5%8F%A3%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="简化了计算，标准化程度提高，有利于预制构件、缩短工期，程式化程度加大了。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8C%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E9%A2%84%E5%88%B6%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E7%BC%A9%E7%9F%AD%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E5%8C%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="清代承担宫廷建筑设计的是七世世袭的“样房”雷氏家族，人称“样式雷”，他们制作的建筑模型称为“烫样”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E5%AE%AB%E5%BB%B7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%96%E8%A2%AD%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E6%A0%B7%E6%88%BF%E2%80%9D%E9%9B%B7%E6%B0%8F%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E9%9B%B7%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%AC%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E7%83%AB%E6%A0%B7%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="民居、祠堂、会馆书院等民间建筑，尚有少量的明代实物遗存，主要是清代的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E3%80%81%E7%A5%A0%E5%A0%82%E3%80%81%E4%BC%9A%E9%A6%86%E4%B9%A6%E9%99%A2%E7%AD%89%E6%B0%91%E9%97%B4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%9E%E7%89%A9%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="其中在技术上、艺术上，以及反映时代生活方面，蕴藏着很多宝贵的经验，值得学习汲取。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%81%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%95%B4%E8%97%8F%E7%9D%80%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%9D%E8%B4%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%B1%B2%E5%8F%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这方面的研究探索工作也已然起步，有待于进一步开展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B7%B2%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%85%E4%BA%8E%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="综观此阶段历经600余年，其中元代除受宋代影响外，呈现出若干新的趋向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BC%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8E%86%E7%BB%8F600%E4%BD%99%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E5%87%BA%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%8B%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="明清建筑则成为中国封建社会建筑的最后一个高潮。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%88%99%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明代在经历数个少数民族统治的朝代之后以一切恢复正统为国策，在建筑方面制定了各类建筑的等级标准。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%AA%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B0%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%A3%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%BD%E7%AD%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明代修建的紫禁城宫殿、天坛、太庙、陵墓等都是规则严整的杰出之作。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E5%9D%9B%E3%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E5%BA%99%E3%80%81%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E7%AD%89%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%B0%E5%87%BA%E4%B9%8B%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="清代的造园和创造出体量极大的汉藏混合式建筑也是值得肯定的发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E5%92%8C%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BA%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8F%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%89%E8%97%8F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第二节     中国古代建筑的特征" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）木构架体系，“墙倒屋不塌”" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%A2%99%E5%80%92%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%A1%8C%E2%80%9D%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国建筑中的重要建筑都是采用木构架的，墙只起围护作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%99%E5%8F%AA%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%B4%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="木构架的主要类型有抬梁式、穿斗式两种。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%9C%89%E6%8A%AC%E6%A2%81%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BF%E6%96%97%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="由此体系而派生出以下特点：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E6%AD%A4%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%80%8C%E6%B4%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.重视台基" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="为防止木柱根部受潮（包括土墙）需台基高出地面。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E6%9C%A8%E6%9F%B1%E6%A0%B9%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%97%E6%BD%AE%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9C%9F%E5%A2%99%EF%BC%89%E9%9C%80%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="逐渐台基的高低与形式成为显示建筑物等级的标志。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如王府台基高度有规定、太和殿用三层须弥座汉白玉台基等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E7%8E%8B%E5%BA%9C%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E6%AE%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%E9%A1%BB%E5%BC%A5%E5%BA%A7%E6%B1%89%E7%99%BD%E7%8E%89%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="台基露出地面的部分称为台明。在宋代《营造法式》中有四种地盘概念，即单槽、双槽、分心槽和金箱斗底槽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%B0%E5%9F%BA%E9%9C%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%B0%E6%98%8E%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%98%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%8D%95%E6%A7%BD%E3%80%81%E5%8F%8C%E6%A7%BD%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%BF%83%E6%A7%BD%E5%92%8C%E9%87%91%E7%AE%B1%E6%96%97%E5%BA%95%E6%A7%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="辽代建筑山西应县佛宫寺释迦塔、天津蓟县独乐寺观音阁及山西五台唐代遗构佛光寺东大殿都是金箱斗底槽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BE%BD%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%BA%94%E5%8E%BF%E4%BD%9B%E5%AE%AB%E5%AF%BA%E9%87%8A%E8%BF%A6%E5%A1%94%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E8%93%9F%E5%8E%BF%E7%8B%AC%E4%B9%90%E5%AF%BA%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E9%98%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E9%81%97%E6%9E%84%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%87%91%E7%AE%B1%E6%96%97%E5%BA%95%E6%A7%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="按柱网分布，一般明清建筑平面由明间（宋称当心间）、次间、稍间、尽间等对称构成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8C%89%E6%9F%B1%E7%BD%91%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%B1%E6%98%8E%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%8B%E7%A7%B0%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%AC%A1%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E7%A8%8D%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E5%B0%BD%E9%97%B4%E7%AD%89%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.屋身灵活" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%B1%8B%E8%BA%AB%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="由于墙不承重，可以任意设置或取消，可亭可仓可室可厅。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E5%A2%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%AD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%93%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%A4%E5%8F%AF%E5%8E%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="墙体可厚可薄，开窗可大可小，以适应各种不同的使用要求与气候。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A2%99%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%AF%E5%8E%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%96%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%80%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%8E%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="屋身墙体及檐柱，汉唐至宋元时期注重使用侧脚（角）与收分（又称收溜）做法，以提高建筑稳定性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%8B%E8%BA%AB%E5%A2%99%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E6%AA%90%E6%9F%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%89%E5%94%90%E8%87%B3%E5%AE%8B%E5%85%83%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BE%A7%E8%84%9A%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%92%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8E%E6%94%B6%E5%88%86%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%88%E7%A7%B0%E6%94%B6%E6%BA%9C%EF%BC%89%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="柱身收分在明清时期逐渐取代唐宋梭柱流行的卷杀做法，工匠口诀“溜多少，升多少”即指侧脚与收溜做法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9F%B1%E8%BA%AB%E6%94%B6%E5%88%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E5%94%90%E5%AE%8B%E6%A2%AD%E6%9F%B1%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B7%E6%9D%80%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E5%8F%A3%E8%AF%80%E2%80%9C%E6%BA%9C%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%87%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E2%80%9D%E5%8D%B3%E6%8C%87%E4%BE%A7%E8%84%9A%E4%B8%8E%E6%94%B6%E6%BA%9C%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.屋顶呈曲线或曲面" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%91%88%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%E6%88%96%E6%9B%B2%E9%9D%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="“上欲尊，而宇欲卑，吐水疾而雷远。”" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8A%E6%AC%B2%E5%B0%8A%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%AE%87%E6%AC%B2%E5%8D%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%90%E6%B0%B4%E7%96%BE%E8%80%8C%E9%9B%B7%E8%BF%9C%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="屋顶以举折或举架形成上陡下缓的坡度曲线，以取得屋面雨水以最快的速度下注而远离屋身。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BE%E6%8A%98%E6%88%96%E4%B8%BE%E6%9E%B6%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%A1%E4%B8%8B%E7%BC%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E5%B1%8B%E9%9D%A2%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E6%B3%A8%E8%80%8C%E8%BF%9C%E7%A6%BB%E5%B1%8B%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="檐部平缓又取得“反宇向阳”多纳日照的好处。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AA%90%E9%83%A8%E5%B9%B3%E7%BC%93%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%8D%E5%AE%87%E5%90%91%E9%98%B3%E2%80%9D%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%B3%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国建筑的曲线坡屋顶有如建筑的冠冕，优美而实惠。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%E5%9D%A1%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%86%A0%E5%86%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E8%80%8C%E5%AE%9E%E6%83%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="屋角起翘、“如鸟斯革、如屋顶翼角有“冲三翘四”之说。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%8B%E8%A7%92%E8%B5%B7%E7%BF%98%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E5%A6%82%E9%B8%9F%E6%96%AF%E9%9D%A9%E3%80%81%E5%A6%82%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E7%BF%BC%E8%A7%92%E6%9C%89%E2%80%9C%E5%86%B2%E4%B8%89%E7%BF%98%E5%9B%9B%E2%80%9D%E4%B9%8B%E8%AF%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="组合屋顶在宋代多见，如清代尚存的十字脊等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%9A%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%9A%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E8%84%8A%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="屋顶除硬山、悬山、攒尖、歇山及庑殿之外，还有盔顶、囤顶、半坡及孟顶（平顶）等多种做法；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E9%99%A4%E7%A1%AC%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%81%E6%82%AC%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%81%E6%94%92%E5%B0%96%E3%80%81%E6%AD%87%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%8A%E5%BA%91%E6%AE%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%94%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E5%9B%A4%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%8A%E5%AD%9F%E9%A1%B6%EF%BC%88%E5%B9%B3%E9%A1%B6%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="民间及园林建筑中常有勾连搭或度做法，以解决大空间问题；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B0%91%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E5%8B%BE%E8%BF%9E%E6%90%AD%E6%88%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="另有砖石生土发券、穹窿及无梁殿做法等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E7%A0%96%E7%9F%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%88%B8%E3%80%81%E7%A9%B9%E7%AA%BF%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%A0%E6%A2%81%E6%AE%BF%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.重要建筑使用斗棋" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="斗棋原为起承重作用的构件，随着结构功能的变化，斗棋成为建筑物等级的标志。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%BA%E8%B5%B7%E6%89%BF%E9%87%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="斗棋按位置主要分为柱头科、平身科及角科，分别对应《营造法式》的柱头铺作、补间铺作和转角铺作。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E6%8C%89%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%9F%B1%E5%A4%B4%E7%A7%91%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E8%BA%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%92%E7%A7%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%9F%B1%E5%A4%B4%E9%93%BA%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%81%E8%A1%A5%E9%97%B4%E9%93%BA%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E8%BD%AC%E8%A7%92%E9%93%BA%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="单“攒”单“朵”斗棋可分解为斗形（斗、升）、弓形（棋类）、方形截面（枋类）和板类四大构件类型。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%95%E2%80%9C%E6%94%92%E2%80%9D%E5%8D%95%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%B5%E2%80%9D%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%97%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%88%E6%96%97%E3%80%81%E5%8D%87%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%BC%93%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%88%E6%A3%8B%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%AA%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%88%E6%9E%8B%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%BF%E7%B1%BB%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="斗棋可使屋檐出挑深远，并具有较好的装饰作用；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%BF%E5%B1%8B%E6%AA%90%E5%87%BA%E6%8C%91%E6%B7%B1%E8%BF%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%BE%83%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="此外，它还具有突出的抗震性能，也是唐宋至明清官式建筑定义下的典型等级象征。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E8%BF%98%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E9%9C%87%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%94%90%E5%AE%8B%E8%87%B3%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E5%AE%98%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E8%B1%A1%E5%BE%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5.装饰构造而不去构造装饰" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8E%BB%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="仅对必需的构造加以艺术处理，而不是另外添加装饰物。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%85%E5%AF%B9%E5%BF%85%E9%9C%80%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E7%89%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如在石柱础上加以雕饰，梁、柱做卷杀，形成梭柱、月梁。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%9C%A8%E7%9F%B3%E6%9F%B1%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%95%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%A2%81%E3%80%81%E6%9F%B1%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%B7%E6%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E6%A2%AD%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%81%E6%9C%88%E6%A2%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="屋顶尖端接缝处加屋脊。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E5%B0%96%E7%AB%AF%E6%8E%A5%E7%BC%9D%E5%A4%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%B1%8B%E8%84%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="脊端、屋檐等有穿钉处加设吻兽、垂兽、仙人走兽、帽钉等以防雨、防滑落。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%84%8A%E7%AB%AF%E3%80%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%AA%90%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%89%E7%A9%BF%E9%92%89%E5%A4%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%BE%E5%90%BB%E5%85%BD%E3%80%81%E5%9E%82%E5%85%BD%E3%80%81%E4%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%BD%E3%80%81%E5%B8%BD%E9%92%89%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%B2%E9%9B%A8%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%BB%91%E8%90%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="甚至油漆彩画也是由于木材需要防腐而引起的，在必需的条件下，加以美化处理，而非纯粹的装饰。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9A%E8%87%B3%E6%B2%B9%E6%BC%86%E5%BD%A9%E7%94%BB%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%90%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%98%B2%E8%85%90%E8%80%8C%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BF%85%E9%9C%80%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%9E%E7%BA%AF%E7%B2%B9%E7%9A%84%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）院落式布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E5%BC%8F%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="用单体建筑围合成院落，建筑群以中轴线为基准由若干院落组合，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9B%B4%E5%90%88%E6%88%90%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E5%87%86%E7%94%B1%E8%8B%A5%E5%B9%B2%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="利用单体建筑的体量大小和在院中所居位置来区别尊卑内外，符合中国封建社会的宗法观念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%9D%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E5%B0%8A%E5%8D%91%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国的宫殿、庙宇、衙署、住宅都属院落式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%BA%99%E5%AE%87%E3%80%81%E8%A1%99%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E9%83%BD%E5%B1%9E%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="另外，院落式平房比单幢的高层木楼阁在防救火灾方面大为有利。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E5%BC%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%88%BF%E6%AF%94%E5%8D%95%E5%B9%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E6%9C%A8%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E5%9C%A8%E9%98%B2%E6%95%91%E7%81%AB%E7%81%BE%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）有规划的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="历史上大多数朝代的都城都比附于《周礼考工记》的王城之制，虽不是完全体现，但大多数都是外形方正，街道平直，按一定规划建造的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E6%9C%9D%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E9%83%BD%E6%AF%94%E9%99%84%E4%BA%8E%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%99%BD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%96%E5%BD%A2%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="包括州县等城市也是如此。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B7%9E%E5%8E%BF%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="只有在自然条件极为特殊的地段，才偶然有不规则形状的城存在。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%9E%81%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E5%81%B6%E7%84%B6%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）山水式园林" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%BC%8F%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国园林园景构图采用曲折的自由布局，因借自然，模仿自然，与中国的山水画、山水诗文有共同的意境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%9B%AD%E6%99%AF%E6%9E%84%E5%9B%BE%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%9B%B2%E6%8A%98%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E5%80%9F%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%A8%A1%E4%BB%BF%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E7%94%BB%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E8%AF%97%E6%96%87%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="与欧洲大陆的古典园林惯用的几何图形、树木修剪、人为造作的气氛，大异其趣。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E6%83%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E6%A0%91%E6%9C%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%89%AA%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%94%E6%B0%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%BC%82%E5%85%B6%E8%B6%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="强调“虽由人作，宛自天开”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E2%80%9C%E8%99%BD%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9B%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%BC%80%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）特有的建筑观" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%A7%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="视建筑等同于舆服车马，不求永存。从来不把建筑作为一种学术。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%86%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%E8%88%86%E6%9C%8D%E8%BD%A6%E9%A9%AC%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%B8%E5%AD%98%E3%80%82%E4%BB%8E%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%8A%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="崇尚俭朴，把“大兴土木”一贯列为劳民伤财的事。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B4%87%E5%B0%9A%E4%BF%AD%E6%9C%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E5%9C%9F%E6%9C%A8%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%80%E8%B4%AF%E5%88%97%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%A4%E8%B4%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对于崇伟新巧的建筑，贬多于褒。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%B4%87%E4%BC%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%B4%AC%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%8E%E8%A4%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="技术由师徒相传，以实地操作、心传口授为主。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%B8%88%E5%BE%92%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E5%9C%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%81%E5%BF%83%E4%BC%A0%E5%8F%A3%E6%8E%88%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="读书人很少有人关心建筑，术书极少，这些建筑观影响了中国建筑的进步。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%B3%E5%BF%83%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AF%E4%B9%A6%E6%9E%81%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%A7%82%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第三节     中国建筑历史知识" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="都城的制度。“匠人营国，方九里，旁三门，国中九经九纬，经涂九轨，左祖右社，面朝后市……”（《周礼·考工记·匠人》）（图）4-1）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E2%80%9C%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E8%90%A5%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B9%E4%B9%9D%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%81%E4%B8%89%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%9D%E7%BB%8F%E4%B9%9D%E7%BA%AC%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B6%82%E4%B9%9D%E8%BD%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A6%E7%A5%96%E5%8F%B3%E7%A4%BE%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%C2%B7%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%894-1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国历代都城规模大小的顺序：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8E%86%E4%BB%A3%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①隋大兴城（唐长安城，图4-2）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E9%9A%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B4%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%94%90%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BE4-2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②北魏洛阳城（图4-3）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③明、清北京城（图4-4、图4-5）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-4%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE4-5%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④元大都（图4-6）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-6%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑤隋、唐洛阳；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A4%E9%9A%8B%E3%80%81%E5%94%90%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑥明南京城（图4-7）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A5%E6%98%8E%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-7%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑦汉长安城（图4-8）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A6%E6%B1%89%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="中国第一座轮廓方正的都城曹魏邺城（图4-9）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E8%BD%AE%E5%BB%93%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E6%9B%B9%E9%AD%8F%E9%82%BA%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="北宋东京平面想象图（图4-10）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%8B%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%AC%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E6%83%B3%E8%B1%A1%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-10%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国五大古都：西安、洛阳、开封、南京、北京；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%A4%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%9A%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%89%E3%80%81%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E3%80%81%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%81%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国七大古都：以上五处加安阳、杭州。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%A4%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B3%E3%80%81%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="金中都、元大都、明清北京城址变迁图（应会默画）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%BD%E3%80%81%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E3%80%81%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%E5%9D%80%E5%8F%98%E8%BF%81%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E4%BC%9A%E9%BB%98%E7%94%BB%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元大都是与周礼考工记王城之制最接近的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%80%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="列入世界文化遗产的中国城市：平遥古城、丽江古城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%A5%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BD%E6%B1%9F%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="唐长安城为里坊制，为封闭型，宋汴梁、临安转变为开放型，沿街设市，沿巷建住房。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%BA%E9%87%8C%E5%9D%8A%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%E3%80%81%E4%B8%B4%E5%AE%89%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%BF%E8%A1%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%BF%E5%B7%B7%E5%BB%BA%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）宫殿" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="周制三朝五门：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%91%A8%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%9D%E4%BA%94%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="三朝：外朝——决定国家大事，治朝——王视事之朝，内朝——办理皇族内部事务、宴会。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%9D%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%96%E6%9C%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%BB%E6%9C%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E7%8E%8B%E8%A7%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E6%9C%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8A%9E%E7%90%86%E7%9A%87%E6%97%8F%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B4%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="五门：皋门、库门、维门、应门、路门。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%9A%E7%9A%8B%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E5%BA%93%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E5%BA%94%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%AF%E9%97%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="东西堂制：大朝居中，两侧为常朝。汉代开东西堂制之先声，晋、南北朝（北周除外）均行东西堂制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%A0%82%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%9D%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%A4%E4%BE%A7%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%82%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%A0%82%E5%88%B6%E4%B9%8B%E5%85%88%E5%A3%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%8B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%97%E5%91%A8%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%89%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%A0%82%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="隋及以后均行三朝纵列之周制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%9D%E7%BA%B5%E5%88%97%E4%B9%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="隋、唐的三朝五门：承天门、太极门、朱明门、两仪门、甘露门。外朝承天门、中朝太极殿、内朝两仪殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E3%80%81%E5%94%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%9D%E4%BA%94%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%BF%E5%A4%A9%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E6%9E%81%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E6%9C%B1%E6%98%8E%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E4%B8%A4%E4%BB%AA%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E7%94%98%E9%9C%B2%E9%97%A8%E3%80%82%E5%A4%96%E6%9C%9D%E6%89%BF%E5%A4%A9%E9%97%A8%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9D%E5%A4%AA%E6%9E%81%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%86%85%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%A4%E4%BB%AA%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="唐代宫殿雄伟，尺度大。大明宫主殿含元殿建于龙首原上，前有长达75m的龙尾道。麟德殿面积达5000余平方米，约为清太和殿的3倍（图4-11）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E9%9B%84%E4%BC%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%82%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%AB%E4%B8%BB%E6%AE%BF%E5%90%AB%E5%85%83%E6%AE%BF%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%8E%E9%BE%99%E9%A6%96%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E9%95%BF%E8%BE%BE75m%E7%9A%84%E9%BE%99%E5%B0%BE%E9%81%93%E3%80%82%E9%BA%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%AE%BF%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%BE%BE5000%E4%BD%99%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A6%E4%B8%BA%E6%B8%85%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%843%E5%80%8D%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-11%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋代宫殿创造性发展是御街千步廊制度。另一特点是使用工字形殿。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%A1%E8%A1%97%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%A5%E5%BB%8A%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E6%AE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="轴心舍：即工字形殿的唐代名称，用于官署。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BD%B4%E5%BF%83%E8%88%8D%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%B3%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元代宫殿喜用工字形殿：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%E5%96%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="受游牧生活、喇嘛教及西亚建筑影响，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%97%E6%B8%B8%E7%89%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E3%80%81%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E6%95%99%E5%8F%8A%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="用多种色彩的琉璃，金、红色装饰，挂毡毯毛皮帷幕。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%91%E3%80%81%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%82%E6%AF%A1%E6%AF%AF%E6%AF%9B%E7%9A%AE%E5%B8%B7%E5%B9%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建孟顶殿，棕毛殿，畏吾儿殿，石造浴室等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%9F%E9%A1%B6%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%A3%95%E6%AF%9B%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E7%95%8F%E5%90%BE%E5%84%BF%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E7%9F%B3%E9%80%A0%E6%B5%B4%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明、清紫禁城宫殿（应做全面了解），清北京故宫总平面如图4-12所示。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E5%81%9A%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%95%85%E5%AE%AB%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%A6%82%E5%9B%BE4-12%E6%89%80%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）坛庙" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9D%9B%E5%BA%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="坛。祭祀天、地、日、月、桑、农等自然物的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9D%9B%E3%80%82%E7%A5%AD%E7%A5%80%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E3%80%81%E6%9C%88%E3%80%81%E6%A1%91%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E7%AD%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="庙。祭祀帝王祖先的建筑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%99%E3%80%82%E7%A5%AD%E7%A5%80%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="大祭，皇帝亲自祭祀。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E7%A5%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%9D%E4%BA%B2%E8%87%AA%E7%A5%AD%E7%A5%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中祭，皇帝派大臣代祭。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E7%A5%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%9D%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E4%BB%A3%E7%A5%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="望祭，不设庙，只朝所祭方向遥祭。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%9B%E7%A5%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%BE%E5%BA%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%9D%E6%89%80%E7%A5%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E9%81%A5%E7%A5%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="圈丘。祭天的坛。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%88%E4%B8%98%E3%80%82%E7%A5%AD%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="天坛（图4-13、图4-14）（应了解其历史概况，默绘其总平面示意图，指出其设计成功之处）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A9%E5%9D%9B%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-13%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE4-14%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%85%B6%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E9%BB%98%E7%BB%98%E5%85%B6%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B6%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%84%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="孔庙（应了解孔庙布局的特点）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AD%94%E5%BA%99%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%AD%94%E5%BA%99%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）陵墓" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="四出羡道。商、周帝王陵墓的形制，由东西南北四方，以斜坡道及踏步由地面通向墓室（图4-15）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%9B%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%A1%E9%81%93%E3%80%82%E5%95%86%E3%80%81%E5%91%A8%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%9C%E5%9D%A1%E9%81%93%E5%8F%8A%E8%B8%8F%E6%AD%A5%E7%94%B1%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E9%80%9A%E5%90%91%E5%A2%93%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-15%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="封土。帝王陵墓地表以上陵体。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%81%E5%9C%9F%E3%80%82%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%B5%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="方上。累土为堆，呈截顶方锥体形的封土。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%E7%B4%AF%E5%9C%9F%E4%B8%BA%E5%A0%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%88%E6%88%AA%E9%A1%B6%E6%96%B9%E9%94%A5%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%81%E5%9C%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="中国已发现最早的一幅建筑总平面图：河北平山县战国中山国王馨墓出土的一块铜板兆域图。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%B1%E5%8E%BF%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%8B%E9%A6%A8%E5%A2%93%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%9D%97%E9%93%9C%E6%9D%BF%E5%85%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="兆域。墓地的界址。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%86%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%82%E5%A2%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%95%8C%E5%9D%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="黄肠题凑。汉代帝王陵制，用栖木段垒成墓室，柜木心为黄色，木段头皆朝内，故称。陵邑。汉陵各设陵邑，即小城市。迁各地豪富及前朝官吏来居住，名为守陵，实是强干弱枝，便于管理统治。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%BB%84%E8%82%A0%E9%A2%98%E5%87%91%E3%80%82%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E9%99%B5%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E6%A0%96%E6%9C%A8%E6%AE%B5%E5%9E%92%E6%88%90%E5%A2%93%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%9C%E6%9C%A8%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%A8%E6%AE%B5%E5%A4%B4%E7%9A%86%E6%9C%9D%E5%86%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E9%99%B5%E9%82%91%E3%80%82%E6%B1%89%E9%99%B5%E5%90%84%E8%AE%BE%E9%99%B5%E9%82%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%E8%BF%81%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E8%B1%AA%E5%AF%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9D%E5%AE%98%E5%90%8F%E6%9D%A5%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%88%E9%99%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%BA%E5%B9%B2%E5%BC%B1%E6%9E%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="唐代陵墓。“因山为穴”（以乾陵为例，解其布局特点）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E9%99%B5%E5%A2%93%E3%80%82%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%A0%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%BA%E7%A9%B4%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B9%BE%E9%99%B5%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="五音姓利。阴阳堪舆术先按姓分属五音）（宫、商、角、徵、羽）而择地不同。宋代国姓赵，属角音，墓地要“东南地穹、西北地垂”，故宋陵由高向低而建。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E9%9F%B3%E5%A7%93%E5%88%A9%E3%80%82%E9%98%B4%E9%98%B3%E5%A0%AA%E8%88%86%E6%9C%AF%E5%85%88%E6%8C%89%E5%A7%93%E5%88%86%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%94%E9%9F%B3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%AB%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E3%80%81%E8%A7%92%E3%80%81%E5%BE%B5%E3%80%81%E7%BE%BD%EF%BC%89%E8%80%8C%E6%8B%A9%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%9B%BD%E5%A7%93%E8%B5%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%9E%E8%A7%92%E9%9F%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%93%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%81%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%97%E5%9C%B0%E7%A9%B9%E3%80%81%E8%A5%BF%E5%8C%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9E%82%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%AE%8B%E9%99%B5%E7%94%B1%E9%AB%98%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8E%E8%80%8C%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明十三陵。选址、布局、单体建筑均具很高水平（图4-16）（应对其作评述）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E9%99%B5%E3%80%82%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E3%80%81%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9D%87%E5%85%B7%E5%BE%88%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-16%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%AF%84%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）宗教建筑" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="佛寺布局的演变：以塔为主，前塔后殿，塔殿并列，塔另置别院或山门前，塔可有可无。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A5%E5%A1%94%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%8D%E5%A1%94%E5%90%8E%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%94%E6%AE%BF%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%94%E5%8F%A6%E7%BD%AE%E5%88%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%88%96%E5%B1%B1%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%94%E5%8F%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E6%97%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="明、清佛寺建筑典型布局：山门，钟鼓楼，天王殿，大雄宝殿，配殿，藏经楼，另附各种院。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%B1%B1%E9%97%A8%EF%BC%8C%E9%92%9F%E9%BC%93%E6%A5%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%84%E5%AE%9D%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E9%85%8D%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E8%97%8F%E7%BB%8F%E6%A5%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A6%E9%99%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E9%99%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="佛教四大名山：①山西五台山（文殊菩萨道场）；②四川峨眉山（普贤菩萨道场）；③" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%8D%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%9A%E2%91%A0%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87%E6%AE%8A%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%81%93%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%E2%91%A1%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E5%B3%A8%E7%9C%89%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%88%E6%99%AE%E8%B4%A4%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%81%93%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%E2%91%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="安徽九华山（地藏菩萨道场）；④浙江普陀山（观音菩萨道场）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E4%B9%9D%E5%8D%8E%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%88%E5%9C%B0%E8%97%8F%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%81%93%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%E2%91%A3%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E6%99%AE%E9%99%80%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%81%93%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="道教名山：江西龙虎山，江苏茅山，湖北武当山，四川青城山，山东崂山，陕西华山，江西三清山。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%90%8D%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%9A%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E9%BE%99%E8%99%8E%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%9F%E8%8B%8F%E8%8C%85%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E6%AD%A6%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E9%9D%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E5%B4%82%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%8E%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%89%E6%B8%85%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="对武当山应特别注意，其主峰天柱峰上的石城，名曰“紫禁城”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AD%A6%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%B1%E5%BA%94%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%BB%E5%B3%B0%E5%A4%A9%E6%9F%B1%E5%B3%B0%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8D%E6%9B%B0%E2%80%9C%E7%B4%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="道教建筑之特点：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B9%8B%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="①以“宫”、“观”、“院”等命名，不以寺称；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%AB%E2%80%9D%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E8%A7%82%E2%80%9D%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E9%99%A2%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%AF%BA%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="②所奉神像蓄发长须，穿中式衣袍；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E6%89%80%E5%A5%89%E7%A5%9E%E5%83%8F%E8%93%84%E5%8F%91%E9%95%BF%E9%A1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%A9%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%8D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="③不以塔为膜拜对象；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%A1%94%E4%B8%BA%E8%86%9C%E6%8B%9C%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="④常有洞天福地等园林布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E6%B4%9E%E5%A4%A9%E7%A6%8F%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="伊斯兰教礼拜寺建筑特点：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E5%85%B0%E6%95%99%E7%A4%BC%E6%8B%9C%E5%AF%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①不供偶像；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E4%B8%8D%E4%BE%9B%E5%81%B6%E5%83%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②设向圣地麦加朝拜的龛；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E8%AE%BE%E5%90%91%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E9%BA%A6%E5%8A%A0%E6%9C%9D%E6%8B%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%BE%9B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③不用动物图像做装饰，用可兰经文、植物及几何图案做装饰；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%81%9A%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%B0%E7%BB%8F%E6%96%87%E3%80%81%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%8A%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E5%81%9A%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④设有邦克楼、望月楼、浴室等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E9%82%A6%E5%85%8B%E6%A5%BC%E3%80%81%E6%9C%9B%E6%9C%88%E6%A5%BC%E3%80%81%E6%B5%B4%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="中国伊斯兰教四大寺：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E5%85%B0%E6%95%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①广州怀圣寺（俗名狮子寺）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9E%E6%80%80%E5%9C%A3%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%97%E5%90%8D%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②泉州清净寺（俗名麒麟寺）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E6%B3%89%E5%B7%9E%E6%B8%85%E5%87%80%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%97%E5%90%8D%E9%BA%92%E9%BA%9F%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③杭州真教寺（俗名凤凰寺）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E7%9C%9F%E6%95%99%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%97%E5%90%8D%E5%87%A4%E5%87%B0%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④扬州仙鹤寺。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E6%89%AC%E5%B7%9E%E4%BB%99%E9%B9%A4%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="舍宅为寺：南北朝盛行的社会风尚。致仕之人舍出住宅作佛寺，以前厅为佛殿，后堂为讲堂。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%88%8D%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%BA%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E7%9B%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E9%A3%8E%E5%B0%9A%E3%80%82%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%95%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%88%8D%E5%87%BA%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%BD%9C%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%8E%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%9B%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E5%A0%82%E4%B8%BA%E8%AE%B2%E5%A0%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="最具代表性的著名古建筑（应记其地点、年代、特色）：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9C%80%E5%85%B7%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%85%B6%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%81%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）佛光寺东大殿——山西五台，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="唐大中十一年（公元857年）建，现存最大的唐代木构建筑（图4-17、图4-18）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83857%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-17%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE4-18%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）南禅寺大殿—山西五台，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%97%E7%A6%85%E5%AF%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%AE%BF%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="唐建中三年（公元782年）建，现存最早的木构建筑（图4-19）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83782%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-19%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）隆兴寺摩尼殿—河北正定，北宋皇佑四年（公元1052年）建，四出抱厦，山面朝前（图4-20）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%9A%86%E5%85%B4%E5%AF%BA%E6%91%A9%E5%B0%BC%E6%AE%BF%E2%80%94%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%8B%E7%9A%87%E4%BD%91%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831052%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%9B%E5%87%BA%E6%8A%B1%E5%8E%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%B1%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%9D%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-20%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）独乐寺观音阁及山门一辽统和二年（公元984年）重建，结构合理（图4-21）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%8B%AC%E4%B9%90%E5%AF%BA%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E9%98%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%B1%B1%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%BE%BD%E7%BB%9F%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83984%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-21%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）晋祠圣母殿—山西原，宋崇宁元年（公元1102年）重修，殿前有鱼沼飞梁（图4-22）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%99%8B%E7%A5%A0%E5%9C%A3%E6%AF%8D%E6%AE%BF%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%8E%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E5%B4%87%E5%AE%81%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831102%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8D%E4%BF%AE%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%BF%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E9%B1%BC%E6%B2%BC%E9%A3%9E%E6%A2%81%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-22%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）永乐宫——山西芮城，元中统三年（公元1264年）建，殿内壁画极珍贵。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%90%E5%AE%AB%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E8%8A%AE%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831264%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%BF%E5%86%85%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%E6%9E%81%E7%8F%8D%E8%B4%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）清净寺一—福建泉州，元至正年间（公元1341~1370年）重修，保持外来影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E6%B8%85%E5%87%80%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E6%B3%89%E5%B7%9E%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E8%87%B3%E6%AD%A3%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831341~1370%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8D%E4%BF%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%96%E6%9D%A5%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（8）布达拉宫一—西藏拉萨，清顺治二年（公元1645年）重建，最大的喇嘛教寺院。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%BE%E6%8B%89%E5%AE%AB%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E6%8B%89%E8%90%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E9%A1%BA%E6%B2%BB%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831645%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E6%95%99%E5%AF%BA%E9%99%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（9）席力图召——内蒙古呼和浩特市，清康熙三十五年（公元1696年）重建，汉藏混合式喇嘛庙。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%AD%E5%8A%9B%E5%9B%BE%E5%8F%AC%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%86%85%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E5%91%BC%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%A9%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E5%BA%B7%E7%86%99%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E5%85%831696%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%89%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%89%E8%97%8F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%BC%8F%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E5%BA%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国佛塔的五种主要类型（举例，绘示意图）：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BD%9B%E5%A1%94%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%98%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）楼阁式塔——山西应县佛宫寺释迦塔（图4-23）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%BA%94%E5%8E%BF%E4%BD%9B%E5%AE%AB%E5%AF%BA%E9%87%8A%E8%BF%A6%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-23%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）密檐塔—河南登封嵩岳寺塔（图4-24）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%86%E6%AA%90%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%81%E5%B5%A9%E5%B2%B3%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-24%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）单层塔——山东济南神通寺四门塔（图4-25）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%95%E5%B1%82%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C%E6%B5%8E%E5%8D%97%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A%E5%AF%BA%E5%9B%9B%E9%97%A8%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-25%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）喇嘛塔——北京妙应寺白塔（图4-26）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A6%99%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%BA%E7%99%BD%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-26%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）金刚宝座式塔——北京大正觉寺金刚宝座塔（图4-27）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E5%AE%9D%E5%BA%A7%E5%BC%8F%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%89%E5%AF%BA%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E5%AE%9D%E5%BA%A7%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-27%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="其他名塔：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%90%8D%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="河北定县开元寺料敌塔——宋塔，现存最高的砖塔，高84m；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%8E%BF%E5%BC%80%E5%85%83%E5%AF%BA%E6%96%99%E6%95%8C%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%8B%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%96%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%9884m%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="河南开封祐国寺塔—宋塔，俗称铁塔，是第一座砌琉璃面砖的塔；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%E7%A5%90%E5%9B%BD%E5%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%8B%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E9%93%81%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E7%A0%8C%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E9%9D%A2%E7%A0%96%E7%9A%84%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="福建泉州开元寺双石塔—宋塔，是现存最高的石塔；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E6%B3%89%E5%B7%9E%E5%BC%80%E5%85%83%E5%AF%BA%E5%8F%8C%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%8B%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%A1%94%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="南京报恩寺琉璃塔——明建，已毁，被当时誉为世界建筑七大奇迹之一；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%A5%E6%81%A9%E5%AF%BA%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%98%8E%E5%BB%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E6%AF%81%EF%BC%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E8%AA%89%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%87%E8%BF%B9%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="河北正定广惠寺华塔——造型华丽，是塔的一种类型，也可视为金刚宝座。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%BF%E6%83%A0%E5%AF%BA%E5%8D%8E%E5%A1%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%A1%94%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%BA%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E5%AE%9D%E5%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="经幢—河北赵县陀罗尼经幢（图4-28）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%8F%E5%B9%A2%E2%80%94%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E8%B5%B5%E5%8E%BF%E9%99%80%E7%BD%97%E5%B0%BC%E7%BB%8F%E5%B9%A2%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-28%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="石窟寺——在山崖上开凿出来的洞窟形佛寺。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%B1%E5%B4%96%E4%B8%8A%E5%BC%80%E5%87%BF%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%9E%E7%AA%9F%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="著名石窟寺：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="甘肃敦煌石窟，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%98%E8%82%83%E6%95%A6%E7%85%8C%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="山西大同云冈石窟，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%86%88%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="河南洛阳龙门石窟，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%E9%BE%99%E9%97%A8%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="山西太原天龙山石窟，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%8E%9F%E5%A4%A9%E9%BE%99%E5%B1%B1%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="甘肃天水麦积山石窟，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%98%E8%82%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E9%BA%A6%E7%A7%AF%E5%B1%B1%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="新疆拜城克孜尔石窟。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E6%8B%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%85%8B%E5%AD%9C%E5%B0%94%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（六）住宅" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="了解古代住宅依靠的间接资料：文献，图画，壁画，画像石，画像砖，明器。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%BE%9D%E9%9D%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BE%E7%94%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%81%E7%94%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%BB%E5%83%8F%E7%9F%B3%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%BB%E5%83%8F%E7%A0%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E5%99%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="唐代的住宅制度：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="《唐会要·舆服志》：“……王公以下舍屋不得施重棋藻井，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%94%90%E4%BC%9A%E8%A6%81%C2%B7%E8%88%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%BF%97%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%88%8D%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E6%96%BD%E9%87%8D%E6%A3%8B%E8%97%BB%E4%BA%95%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="三品以上堂屋不得过五间九架、厅厦两头，门屋不得过五间五架。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E5%93%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%A0%82%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%94%E9%97%B4%E4%B9%9D%E6%9E%B6%E3%80%81%E5%8E%85%E5%8E%A6%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%B4%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%A8%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%94%E9%97%B4%E4%BA%94%E6%9E%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="五品以上堂舍不得过三间五架，门屋不得过一间两架……士庶公私第宅皆不得造楼阁临视人家。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E5%93%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%A0%82%E8%88%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%89%E9%97%B4%E4%BA%94%E6%9E%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%A8%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%80%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%A4%E6%9E%B6%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B6%E5%85%AC%E7%A7%81%E7%AC%AC%E5%AE%85%E7%9A%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%BC%E9%98%81%E4%B8%B4%E8%A7%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="……又庶人所造堂舍不得过三间四架，门屋一间两架，仍不得辄施装饰。”" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6%E5%8F%88%E5%BA%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%80%E9%80%A0%E5%A0%82%E8%88%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%89%E9%97%B4%E5%9B%9B%E6%9E%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%A8%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%80%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%A4%E6%9E%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%BE%84%E6%96%BD%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="现存明代住宅，在山西、安徽、江西、浙江、福建等地均有遗存。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E5%AD%98%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E3%80%81%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E3%80%81%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E3%80%81%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%89%E9%81%97%E5%AD%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.庭院式住宅" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%BA%AD%E9%99%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）北京四合院：有单进院、二进院、三进院及多进院，通常多是“三正两耳”的“五间口”院落（图4-29）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%88%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%95%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E4%B8%89%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%9A%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A3%E4%B8%A4%E8%80%B3%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%94%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%A3%E2%80%9D%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-29%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）晋陕窄院：大体比例为1.5：1或2：1，单坡屋顶的俗称“四水归一”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%99%8B%E9%99%95%E7%AA%84%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%93%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1.5%EF%BC%9A1%E6%88%962%EF%BC%9A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%95%E5%9D%A1%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%9B%E6%B0%B4%E5%BD%92%E4%B8%80%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）东北大院：以“一正四厢”的两进院为基本型制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%9C%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A3%E5%9B%9B%E5%8E%A2%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）云南“一颗印”：其典型格局是“三间四耳倒八尺”（图4-30）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%91%E5%8D%97%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%97%E5%8D%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B6%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%89%E9%97%B4%E5%9B%9B%E8%80%B3%E5%80%92%E5%85%AB%E5%B0%BA%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-30%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）徽州天井院：可形成带两个天井的二进院，其中间两厅合脊，俗称“一脊翻两堂”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%BE%BD%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%B8%A6%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%A4%E5%8E%85%E5%90%88%E8%84%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E8%84%8A%E7%BF%BB%E4%B8%A4%E5%A0%82%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）浙江天井院：大型天井院以“十三间头”最常见，当地俗称“五凤楼”（图4-31）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E9%99%A2%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%B4%E2%80%9D%E6%9C%80%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%94%E5%87%A4%E6%A5%BC%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-31%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）苏南地区天井院：典型案例有明代的吴县东山尊让堂，平面呈倒“凸”字形（图4-32）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E8%8B%8F%E5%8D%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%90%B4%E5%8E%BF%E4%B8%9C%E5%B1%B1%E5%B0%8A%E8%AE%A9%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%91%88%E5%80%92%E2%80%9C%E5%87%B8%E2%80%9D%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-32%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（8）阅粤天井院：有两种基本型制——“爬狮”、“四点金”，以及由前两者串联构成“三座落”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E9%98%85%E7%B2%A4%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%B6%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E2%80%9C%E7%88%AC%E7%8B%AE%E2%80%9D%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%9B%E7%82%B9%E9%87%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%B1%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%A4%E8%80%85%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E8%90%BD%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.永定客家土楼" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%B0%B8%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%B6%E5%9C%9F%E6%A5%BC%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="永定土楼分为圆楼和方楼两种。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B0%B8%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%9F%E6%A5%BC%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%86%E6%A5%BC%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="圆楼的典型案例有承启楼（图4-33），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%86%E6%A5%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%89%E6%89%BF%E5%90%AF%E6%A5%BC%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-33%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="方楼的典型案例有遗经楼（图4-34）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B9%E6%A5%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%89%E9%81%97%E7%BB%8F%E6%A5%BC%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-34%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.窑洞" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%AA%91%E6%B4%9E%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="分为三种基本类型——靠崖窑、下沉式窑院（地坑院）和砖砌锢窑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%9D%A0%E5%B4%96%E7%AA%91%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%89%E5%BC%8F%E7%AA%91%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%91%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E7%A0%96%E7%A0%8C%E9%94%A2%E7%AA%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="靠崖窑的典型案例有河南巩县康店村中的明清“康百万庄园”窑群（图4-35）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9D%A0%E5%B4%96%E7%AA%91%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%89%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%B7%A9%E5%8E%BF%E5%BA%B7%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E2%80%9C%E5%BA%B7%E7%99%BE%E4%B8%87%E5%BA%84%E5%9B%AD%E2%80%9D%E7%AA%91%E7%BE%A4%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-35%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（七）园林" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%83%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="中西方园林大异其趣。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%BC%82%E5%85%B6%E8%B6%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国园林以表现自然意趣为目的，师法自然，以山水为景观骨干，“虽由人作，宛自天开”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E4%BB%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%84%8F%E8%B6%A3%E4%B8%BA%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%88%E6%B3%95%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%BA%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E9%AA%A8%E5%B9%B2%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E8%99%BD%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9B%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%BC%80%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="与欧洲古典园林追求轴线对称，几何图形，分行列队，树木修剪，显示人力的做法，大不相同。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%97%E9%98%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%91%E6%9C%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%89%AA%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="中国园林发展的五个历史阶段：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%AA%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①汉以前以帝王贵族狩猎苑囿为主体；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%B8%9D%E7%8E%8B%E8%B4%B5%E6%97%8F%E7%8B%A9%E7%8C%8E%E8%8B%91%E5%9B%BF%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②魏、晋、南北朝山水园奠基（园林成为真正的艺术）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E9%AD%8F%E3%80%81%E6%99%8B%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E5%B1%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9B%AD%E5%A5%A0%E5%9F%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③唐代风景园全面发展；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%AD%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④两宋造园普及；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E4%B8%A4%E5%AE%8B%E9%80%A0%E5%9B%AD%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%8A%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑤明、清——园林的最后兴盛时期。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A4%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E5%85%B4%E7%9B%9B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="三山五园——清代皇家在北京西郊所建的园林（图4-38）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%B1%E4%BA%94%E5%9B%AD%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%8A%E6%89%80%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-38%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="瓮山（万寿山）——清漪园（颐和园）玉泉山——静明园" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%93%AE%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%87%E5%AF%BF%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%89%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%B8%85%E6%BC%AA%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88%E9%A2%90%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%89%E6%B3%89%E5%B1%B1%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%9D%99%E6%98%8E%E5%9B%AD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="香山——静宜园畅春园、圆明园" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A6%99%E5%B1%B1%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%9D%99%E5%AE%9C%E5%9B%AD%E7%95%85%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%AD%E3%80%81%E5%9C%86%E6%98%8E%E5%9B%AD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="江南名园：寄畅园（明，无锡），留园（图4-39），拙政园，沧浪亭，狮子林，网师园，环秀山庄（以上苏州），个园、小盘谷（以上扬州），瞻园（南京）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%AF%84%E7%95%85%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E9%94%A1%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%95%99%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-39%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%8B%99%E6%94%BF%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%A7%E6%B5%AA%E4%BA%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E6%9E%97%EF%BC%8C%E7%BD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%AF%E7%A7%80%E5%B1%B1%E5%BA%84%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%8B%8F%E5%B7%9E%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%AD%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%9B%98%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%AC%E5%B7%9E%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%9E%BB%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（八）构造、部件及装修" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AB%EF%BC%89%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E3%80%81%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.木构架的两种主要形式" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E6%9C%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%9E%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）抬梁式（图4-40）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%8A%AC%E6%A2%81%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-40%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）穿斗式（图4-41）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%A9%BF%E6%96%97%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-41%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.屋顶的五种主要形式（图4-42）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%B1%8B%E9%A1%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-42%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）庑殿顶——四阿顶。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BA%91%E6%AE%BF%E9%A1%B6%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%9B%9B%E9%98%BF%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）歇山顶一—九脊顶、厦两头。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%AD%87%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B6%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E4%B9%9D%E8%84%8A%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E5%8E%A6%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）悬山顶——不厦两头。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%82%AC%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B6%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%8E%A6%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）硬山顶。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%A1%AC%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）攒尖顶。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%94%92%E5%B0%96%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="另有孟顶、盔顶等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%9F%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E7%9B%94%E9%A1%B6%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="柱顶石——即柱础的清式名称，柱下的承载构件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%9F%B1%E9%A1%B6%E7%9F%B3%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8D%B3%E6%9F%B1%E7%A1%80%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%85%E5%BC%8F%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%9F%B1%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%89%BF%E8%BD%BD%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="横——柱与础之间的垫，起隔潮作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A8%AA%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%9F%B1%E4%B8%8E%E7%A1%80%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%AB%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%B7%E9%9A%94%E6%BD%AE%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="梭柱——上下端或仅上端做卷杀之柱。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A2%AD%E6%9F%B1%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E7%AB%AF%E6%88%96%E4%BB%85%E4%B8%8A%E7%AB%AF%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%B7%E6%9D%80%E4%B9%8B%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="生起——檐柱由当心间向两端逐间升高，使檐口呈一缓和曲线；宋《营造法式》规定，次间柱升高2寸，以下依次迭增2寸。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%9F%E8%B5%B7%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%AA%90%E6%9F%B1%E7%94%B1%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E9%97%B4%E5%90%91%E4%B8%A4%E7%AB%AF%E9%80%90%E9%97%B4%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E6%AA%90%E5%8F%A3%E5%91%88%E4%B8%80%E7%BC%93%E5%92%8C%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%9B%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%AC%A1%E9%97%B4%E6%9F%B1%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%982%E5%AF%B8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BE%9D%E6%AC%A1%E8%BF%AD%E5%A2%9E2%E5%AF%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="侧脚——宋《营造法式》规定；檐柱向内倾柱高的10/1000，两山檐柱向内倾8/1000，角柱两个方向都倾，以增加建筑物的稳定性。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%A7%E8%84%9A%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9B%E6%AA%90%E6%9F%B1%E5%90%91%E5%86%85%E5%80%BE%E6%9F%B1%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%8410/1000%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%A4%E5%B1%B1%E6%AA%90%E6%9F%B1%E5%90%91%E5%86%85%E5%80%BE8/1000%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%92%E6%9F%B1%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E9%83%BD%E5%80%BE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋《营造法式》的四种地盘图（应会画、会分辨）：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%98%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%94%E4%BC%9A%E7%94%BB%E3%80%81%E4%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①金厢斗底槽；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E9%87%91%E5%8E%A2%E6%96%97%E5%BA%95%E6%A7%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②单槽；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E5%8D%95%E6%A7%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③双槽；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E5%8F%8C%E6%A7%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④分心槽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E5%88%86%E5%BF%83%E6%A7%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="副阶周匝。在主体建筑之外，加一圈回廊，《营造法式》称之为“副阶周匝”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%89%AF%E9%98%B6%E5%91%A8%E5%8C%9D%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%BB%8A%EF%BC%8C%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E7%A7%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%89%AF%E9%98%B6%E5%91%A8%E5%8C%9D%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="普拍方之变化。唐代尚未见，宋开始有，宽于阑额。宽度减小渐与阑额趋于一致。明清时阑额宽，普拍方窄于阑额，改称平板枋。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%8D%E6%96%B9%E4%B9%8B%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%E5%94%90%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%BD%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%91%E9%A2%9D%E3%80%82%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%8F%E6%B8%90%E4%B8%8E%E9%98%91%E9%A2%9D%E8%B6%8B%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E3%80%82%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E6%97%B6%E9%98%91%E9%A2%9D%E5%AE%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%8D%E6%96%B9%E7%AA%84%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%91%E9%A2%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E6%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="斗棋之演变趋势：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%97%E6%A3%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%BC%94%E5%8F%98%E8%B6%8B%E5%8A%BF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="①由大而小；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E7%94%B1%E5%A4%A7%E8%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="②由简而繁；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E7%94%B1%E7%AE%80%E8%80%8C%E7%B9%81%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="③由雄壮而纤巧；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E7%94%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%A3%AE%E8%80%8C%E7%BA%A4%E5%B7%A7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="④由结构的而装饰的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E7%94%B1%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E8%80%8C%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑤由真结构的而假刻的；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A4%E7%94%B1%E7%9C%9F%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E8%80%8C%E5%81%87%E5%88%BB%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="⑥分布由疏朗而繁密。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A5%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%94%B1%E7%96%8F%E6%9C%97%E8%80%8C%E7%B9%81%E5%AF%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="举架与举折——定屋架坡度的方法。清式为举架，由檐部逐步架加大坡度。宋式先定脊博高度，逐步架减小坡度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BE%E6%9E%B6%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%BE%E6%8A%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%9A%E5%B1%8B%E6%9E%B6%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E6%B8%85%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BE%E6%9E%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E6%AA%90%E9%83%A8%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E6%9E%B6%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E5%AE%8B%E5%BC%8F%E5%85%88%E5%AE%9A%E8%84%8A%E5%8D%9A%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E6%9E%B6%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%8F%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="推山与收山：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%A8%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%8E%E6%94%B6%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="推山是加长院殿顶正脊长度的做法。有推山的年代晚（明及以后）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%A8%E5%B1%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%8A%A0%E9%95%BF%E9%99%A2%E6%AE%BF%E9%A1%B6%E6%AD%A3%E8%84%8A%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E6%9C%89%E6%8E%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%99%9A%EF%BC%88%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="收山是歇山顶两山向内收进的做法，收进大的年代早，清代只收进一模径。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%94%B6%E5%B1%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%87%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B6%E4%B8%A4%E5%B1%B1%E5%90%91%E5%86%85%E6%94%B6%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%BF%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%97%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%8F%AA%E6%94%B6%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A1%E5%BE%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="建筑色彩的等级：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="春秋时期一—天子丹，诸侯黝、大夫苍，士黄（黄色），以红色为最尊贵。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E5%A4%A9%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E9%BB%9D%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%AB%E8%8B%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%AB%E9%BB%84%EF%BC%88%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8A%E8%B4%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="清代以黄色为最尊贵，以下次序是：赤、绿、青、蓝、黑、灰。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E4%BB%A5%E9%BB%84%E8%89%B2%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8A%E8%B4%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%AC%A1%E5%BA%8F%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E8%B5%A4%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%92%E3%80%81%E8%93%9D%E3%80%81%E9%BB%91%E3%80%81%E7%81%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="清代彩画三种：（由尊至卑）和玺，旋子，苏式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%BD%A9%E7%94%BB%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%9A%EF%BC%88%E7%94%B1%E5%B0%8A%E8%87%B3%E5%8D%91%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%8B%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%8B%8F%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋式雕刻分类——剔地起突（高浮雕），压地隐起华（浅浮雕），减地平级（线刻），素平。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E5%BC%8F%E9%9B%95%E5%88%BB%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%89%94%E5%9C%B0%E8%B5%B7%E7%AA%81%EF%BC%88%E9%AB%98%E6%B5%AE%E9%9B%95%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%9A%90%E8%B5%B7%E5%8D%8E%EF%BC%88%E6%B5%85%E6%B5%AE%E9%9B%95%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%B9%B3%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%88%E7%BA%BF%E5%88%BB%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%B4%A0%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="正脊两端构件一—晋始用鸱尾，唐鹏尾，宋鹏尾、龙尾、鱼尾，元鸱吻，明、清吻兽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A3%E8%84%8A%E4%B8%A4%E7%AB%AF%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E6%99%8B%E5%A7%8B%E7%94%A8%E9%B8%B1%E5%B0%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%90%E9%B9%8F%E5%B0%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E9%B9%8F%E5%B0%BE%E3%80%81%E9%BE%99%E5%B0%BE%E3%80%81%E9%B1%BC%E5%B0%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E9%B8%B1%E5%90%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B8%85%E5%90%BB%E5%85%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="仙人走兽——《大清会典》规定顺序为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%BD%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E3%80%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%85%E4%BC%9A%E5%85%B8%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="仙人骑鸡、龙、凤、狮子、海马、天马、押鱼、狡貌、解、斗牛。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E9%AA%91%E9%B8%A1%E3%80%81%E9%BE%99%E3%80%81%E5%87%A4%E3%80%81%E7%8B%AE%E5%AD%90%E3%80%81%E6%B5%B7%E9%A9%AC%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E9%A9%AC%E3%80%81%E6%8A%BC%E9%B1%BC%E3%80%81%E7%8B%A1%E8%B2%8C%E3%80%81%E8%A7%A3%E3%80%81%E6%96%97%E7%89%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="走兽共九只，出列时必须为奇数，只有太和殿例外，加了一只“行什”，共十只。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%BD%E5%85%B1%E4%B9%9D%E5%8F%AA%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E5%88%97%E6%97%B6%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%B8%BA%E5%A5%87%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E6%AE%BF%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%AA%E2%80%9C%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%80%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B1%E5%8D%81%E5%8F%AA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="平阎与平棋——小方格的天花板为平阎，年代早。平棋为大方格的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B3%E9%98%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%B3%E6%A3%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%BA%E5%B9%B3%E9%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%97%A9%E3%80%82%E5%B9%B3%E6%A3%8B%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="铺首——门上的供推拉叩门的构件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%93%BA%E9%A6%96%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9B%E6%8E%A8%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%A9%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="嫡首——嫡是龙子之一，在碑首，殿阶上常用石刻成龙首形。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AB%A1%E9%A6%96%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AB%A1%E6%98%AF%E9%BE%99%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%A2%91%E9%A6%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%BF%E9%98%B6%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%BB%E6%88%90%E9%BE%99%E9%A6%96%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="象眼——台阶侧面三角形的部分，宋式象眼层层凹入，《营造法式》规定凹人三层，每层凹入半寸至一寸。另外在中国建筑中凡呈直角三角形的部位常称象眼。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%B1%A1%E7%9C%BC%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8F%B0%E9%98%B6%E4%BE%A7%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E5%BC%8F%E8%B1%A1%E7%9C%BC%E5%B1%82%E5%B1%82%E5%87%B9%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%8C%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%87%B9%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E5%B1%82%E5%87%B9%E5%85%A5%E5%8D%8A%E5%AF%B8%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%AF%B8%E3%80%82%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%A1%E5%91%88%E7%9B%B4%E8%A7%92%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%8D%E5%B8%B8%E7%A7%B0%E8%B1%A1%E7%9C%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="须弥座——尊贵的台座，源于佛教圣山须弥山，用于佛像及佛殿的基座。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A1%BB%E5%BC%A5%E5%BA%A7%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B0%8A%E8%B4%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E%E4%BD%9B%E6%95%99%E5%9C%A3%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%BB%E5%BC%A5%E5%B1%B1%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E4%BD%9B%E5%83%8F%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%9B%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="石柱——北齐义慈惠石柱是位于河北定兴的一处石刻纪念柱。柱顶有一三开间的小殿，殿的歇山顶、梭柱等反映了南北朝建筑的形象（图4-43）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%9F%B3%E6%9F%B1%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%8C%97%E9%BD%90%E4%B9%89%E6%85%88%E6%83%A0%E7%9F%B3%E6%9F%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%88%BB%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E6%9F%B1%E3%80%82%E6%9F%B1%E9%A1%B6%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%80%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%87%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B6%E3%80%81%E6%A2%AD%E6%9F%B1%E7%AD%89%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9D%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE4-43%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（九）其他" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B9%9D%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="历代建筑哲匠：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8E%86%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%93%B2%E5%8C%A0%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="春秋——鲁班，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%B2%81%E7%8F%AD%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="西汉——阳城延，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%B1%89%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E9%98%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="北魏——杨衡之，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%97%E9%AD%8F%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%9D%A8%E8%A1%A1%E4%B9%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="隋——宇文恺，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AE%87%E6%96%87%E6%81%BA%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="五代——喻皓，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%96%BB%E7%9A%93%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宋——李诫，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%9D%8E%E8%AF%AB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明——崩祥，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B4%A9%E7%A5%A5%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="清——样式雷。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%85%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E9%9B%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="古代建筑术书：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%AF%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="《周礼·考工记·匠人》、《木经》，宋《营造法式》，清工部《工程做法则例》、《鲁班营造正式》、《园冶》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%C2%B7%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8B%E3%80%81%E3%80%8A%E6%9C%A8%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%88%99%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E3%80%81%E3%80%8A%E9%B2%81%E7%8F%AD%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%E3%80%81%E3%80%8A%E5%9B%AD%E5%86%B6%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此外，尚有《清式营造则例》及《营造法原》二书，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8A%E6%B8%85%E5%BC%8F%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E5%88%99%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%8A%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8E%9F%E3%80%8B%E4%BA%8C%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="前者为近代建筑学家梁思成研究清式建筑之专著；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%89%8D%E8%80%85%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%91%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E6%A2%81%E6%80%9D%E6%88%90%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%B8%85%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%93%E8%91%97%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="后者为近代建筑营造家姚补云有关江南地区古建筑的讲义，由刘敦桢、张至刚审核、增补。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8E%E8%80%85%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%91%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E5%AE%B6%E5%A7%9A%E8%A1%A5%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%88%98%E6%95%A6%E6%A1%A2%E3%80%81%E5%BC%A0%E8%87%B3%E5%88%9A%E5%AE%A1%E6%A0%B8%E3%80%81%E5%A2%9E%E8%A1%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宋《营造法式》，作者李诫，共34卷，3555条，包括释名、各作制度、功限、料例和图样，是研究我国古代建筑最重要的术书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%90%A5%E9%80%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E6%9D%8E%E8%AF%AB%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B134%E5%8D%B7%EF%BC%8C3555%E6%9D%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%87%8A%E5%90%8D%E3%80%81%E5%90%84%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%8A%9F%E9%99%90%E3%80%81%E6%96%99%E4%BE%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AF%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="明《园冶》作者计成，内容“由绘而园，水石之外，旁及土木”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%98%8E%E3%80%8A%E5%9B%AD%E5%86%B6%E3%80%8B%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%AE%A1%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B1%E7%BB%98%E8%80%8C%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%9F%B3%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%9F%E6%9C%A8%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="下列各名句的出处：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E5%90%84%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%84%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="“凿户腑以为室，当其无，有室之用，故有之以为利，无之以为用。”——老子《道德经》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E5%87%BF%E6%88%B7%E8%85%91%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E5%85%B6%E6%97%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%A4%E4%B9%8B%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E6%9C%89%E4%B9%8B%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E4%B9%8B%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E8%80%81%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8A%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="“天子以四海为家，非壮丽，无以重威”——萧何在向刘邦解释为什么未央宫要建得壮丽时所说。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A9%E5%AD%90%E4%BB%A5%E5%9B%9B%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%A3%AE%E4%B8%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E5%A8%81%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E8%90%A7%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E5%90%91%E5%88%98%E9%82%A6%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%9C%AA%E5%A4%AE%E5%AE%AB%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E5%BE%97%E5%A3%AE%E4%B8%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%89%80%E8%AF%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="“虽由人作，宛自天开”计成在《园冶》中语。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E8%99%BD%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9B%E8%87%AA%E5%A4%A9%E5%BC%80%E2%80%9D%E8%AE%A1%E6%88%90%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%9B%AD%E5%86%B6%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第四节      中国的世界遗产及历史文化名城保护" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%90%8D%E5%9F%8E%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）中国世界文化遗产名录" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%90%8D%E5%BD%95%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="联合国教科文组织将世界遗产分为文化遗产、自然遗产、文化与自然双重遗产三大类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E6%95%99%E7%A7%91%E6%96%87%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%8F%8C%E9%87%8D%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="截至2018年7月2日，伴随中国贵州省梵净山项目的成功申遗（自然遗产），中国已有53个遗产项目列入《世界遗产名录》，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B32018%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%882%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%B4%B5%E5%B7%9E%E7%9C%81%E6%A2%B5%E5%87%80%E5%B1%B1%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%94%B3%E9%81%97%EF%BC%88%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%8953%E4%B8%AA%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%90%8D%E5%BD%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中有文化遗产36项，自然遗产13项，文化与自然双重遗产4项（表4-1）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A736%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A713%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%8F%8C%E9%87%8D%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A74%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%88%E8%A1%A84-1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
